Bio: Born and raised on the track, we create the most advanced performance cars in the world.
Caption text:
This week McLaren Tech Club takes us to Denmark, to our friends at the LEGO HQ. The McLaren Senna GTR is a truly special car. Unique in its aerodynamic capabilities and utterly extreme in its performance, it is truly uncompromising in its approach to lap times. 

Translating something so extreme into LEGO Technic™ was no easy feat, taking all of @lego incredible design processes to produce the amazing LEGO Technic™ McLaren Senna GTR model.

So how did they do it? Aurélien Rouge, Senior Designer at LEGO Technic™ explains the careful and considered design process behind the latest LEGO and McLaren Automotive collaboration.,The contours of the 720S are distinctly McLaren, yet the details are boldly different. Our designers took inspiration from the Great White Shark, a beautifully sleek yet brutally efficient hunting machine.,The 620R, pictured here in the seaside town of Little Hampton, is truly special. It not only looks like a race car, but it also handles, performs and feels like a race car too.,An innovation of the technology first seen in the McLaren P1™ hypercar, the MonoCage II found in the 720S is a one-piece carbon fibre tub that now includes the roof. 

Extending over the engine bay, it includes wider door apertures that open into the roof.,Queen Elizabeth Olympic Park has hosted some of the worlds top performing athletes...and top performance is no stranger to the 720S. It’s blisteringly fast with phenomenal driver engagement. Fitting we enjoy the view.,In the GT, the wraparound glass cabin is designed for you to enjoy all-round views. Hour after hour. Mile after mile.,East London’s trendsetting Shoreditch, is home to edgy and unique art. Acquainted with careful craftmanship the GT's profile is sleek but purposeful. This is a car that invites you to drive.,Our pioneering design gives the new GT a unique beauty and balance. Beneath the fluid surfaces, you’ll find the innovative design and engineering that’s at the heart of every McLaren.,Providing some great driving roads for the McLaren GT to explore, we take a moment to stop in Bristol and admire the view, the GT is a masterpiece of tactile luxury and from the cabin... the view is always great.,Clifton Suspension Bridge, in Bristol, is one of the UK's most recognisable structures. Marking a turning point in the history of engineering; the bridge is iconic to the city. No wonder it has claimed a rightful place in #GTadventures.

——

"The ICONS book is, in a way, the only revealing lens to understand that the catalog of the 50-plus Nike shoes I have designed are in my mind “one shoe." One story." ~ @virgilabloh. 

——
ICONS, published by Taschen, is a dynamic retrospective of the extensive collaborative project between NIKE, Inc. and @virgilabloh.

Underpinned by The Ten, ICONS explores how the partnership works to unify all the intangible cultural threads connected to sneakers. The book traces Abloh’s investigative, creative process through documentation of prototypes, original text messages from Abloh to Nike designers and treasures from the Nike archives.

Bio: Perfil oficial de Arturo Vidal, jugador del  @inter 🇮🇹 y de la Selección Chilena de Fútbol.
Caption text:
Ready, pronti,listos!!! 💪🏽🔥👑😉
Forza @inter 🖤💙 mañana con todo carajo, a seguir por el mismo camino!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽,Muchas Gracias por este lindo vídeo!!!❤️❤️ 👑💪🏽👍🏽😉,👑🤴🏽👑🤴🏽👑,La mia intenzione non è mai stata quella di baciare lo stemma di un altra squadra. Il bacio è stata una dimostrazione di affetto per un fratello che mi ha dato il calcio, con il quale ho vissuto anni meravigliosi insieme e ci vogliamo bene. 
Io rispetto la mia squadra, i nostri tifosi e la gente che ha avuto fiducia in me per difendere e continuare a far crescere la storia di questo bellissimo club. E lascerò l anima per quello! 
Forza @inter !!!🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙,💪🏽🔥 👑 💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Es una pena muy grande esta noticia de que no seguirá trabajando junto a nosotros en este camino al mundial. Se entiende y se respeta, principalmente por la responsabilidad de gente que hace daño al fútbol, como muchos de la prensa mediocre y algunos dirigentes que no entienden nada de nuestra actividad😡 .
Lo quiero mucho, le agradezco infinitamente y le deseo lo mejor a usted y a su cuerpo técnico en el camino que tomen 😢 , gracias por todo este tiempo juntos, por ayudarnos, todo lo que hagamos de acá en adelante también será por y para ustedes. 
Siempre fue un caballero con nosotros,un hombre valiente que tomó el desafío de acompañarnos en un momento difícil y nos ayudó a encontrar las fuerzas para seguir luchando por nuestra querida selección... GRACIAS PROFE ❤️ 🙏🏻
Le deseo lo mejor y nos vemos en Qatar 2022!!! 🇨🇴 🔥 🇨🇱 💪🏽💪🏽,Feliz por el paso a cuartos de copa y por mi primer gol, ahora vendrán muchas más forza @inter 🖤💙💪🏽👑🔥⚽️😉,🔥💪🏽👑 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Mal resultado por cómo se jugó!!😡 pero debemos seguir peleando y trabajando... aun queda mucho!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Pronto per domani 💪🏽Forza @inter 🖤💙 👑💪🏽 🔥 😉👍🏽 ⚽️

Caption text:
@hypegolf: @footjoy has introduced the HyperFlex BOA Golf Shoe featuring high-tech innovation, performance, and supreme comfort. The golf shoe is designed for longevity and features a BOA Fit System that initiates a WRAPID structure that blankets a form fit throughout the foot. Its configuration refines stability in the shoe without sacrificing elasticity. The silhouette is also equipped with a proprietary StratoFoam cushioning system for support, while also catering to a golfer’s need for energy return. These are set to release sometime in February for $180 USD. Click the link in bio for more info.⁠⠀
Photo: Footjoy,@blondey and @adidas have returned for its fourth see-through Superstar collaboration. Taking on a classic “Core Black/Cloud White” colorway, the uppers are crafted from a partially translucent jet black TPU, and overlaid with a white Three Stripe graphic, white heel tab with black branding, and a gold “Blondey” midfoot stamp. Though the upper may appear somewhat delicate at first glimpse, Blondey told HYPEBEAST that it’s in fact much more durable than standard skate shoe materials. Pick up a pair come January 30.⁠⠀
Photo: adidas,@snipes_usa celebrates its new Brooklyn store opening with "Dunks Since 1985" Pop-Up Museum. Nestled in the center of the 6,000 square foot converted bank, the pop-up museum consists of 35 ultra-rare and influential @nike Dunks, ranging from artist collaborations to seminal @nikesb styles and much more all provided by @projectblitz. The display will be on until February 28. Click the link in bio for more info.⁠ Which is your favorite Dunk? 
Photo: Nick Llanton/HYPEBEAST,@newbalance continues its slew of 2002R releases with a duo of colorways. Originally released in 2002 as New Balance’s most innovative running sneaker, this updated 2002R boasts the same brand technologies as the original with the ABZORB cushioning and N-ERGY in the midsole resulting in an almost identical aesthetic. Both pairs feature premium pig suede uppers ensuring the quality that New Balance is known for. Expect these to release within the coming months.⁠⠀
Photo: New Balance,@jumpman23 has unveiled a Spring-ready colorway of the Air Jordan 1 Mid in "Dutch Green." The upper of the shoe is expressed in two tones of green accompanied by pink laces adding a sleek colorblocking to the upper of the shoe. While black Swooshes, pink Jumpman tongue tags, printed Wings motifs on the collars, and insoles serve as a nice touch of detail to finish off the look. Look for these to arrive within the coming weeks.⁠⠀
Photo: Nike,@adidas continues its goal towards sustainability by bringing PRIMEGREEN construction and a playful take on the classic Stan Smith silhouette with Earth-centric graphics reminiscent of Sean Wotherspoon's “Superearth” collaboration. Uppers are built of mostly white leather with the highlight being a colorful collage of graphics that reach from the forefoot to the heel and encompass everything from flowers to raindrops, a globe, and a hand-stenciled Trefoil logo. The shoe is available now via @atmos_japan for approximately $116 USD.⁠⠀
Photo: atmos⁠,A new look at a @sacaiofficial x @jpgaultierofficial x @nike Vaporwaffle has surfaced online as we near Chitose Abe’s debut for Jean Paul Gaultier couture. Sporting a familiar double-stacked midsole and doubled up Swooshes, the couture-focused shoe features an upper that boasts nylon, suede and leather, all split by Air Footscape Woven-like black or white stitching that runs across the midfoot and toebox. Catch it in action during Abe’s first Gaultier runway.⁠⠀
Photo: @sneakerjamz_new,@asics has unveiled a new GEL-QUANTUM 180 silhouette alongside the launch of its Spring/Summer 2021 “ENGINEERED FOR EVERYDAY” campaign. Tapping LA-based photographer @camhicks_ and London-based furniture designer @modularbymensah, the new shoe sees an aesthetic makeover on the upper featuring a mesh toe box with leather overlays similar to their running models. Look for it to come in two colorways on January 22 via the ASICS website and official stockists for approximately $170 USD each.⁠⠀
Photo: ASICS,@jumpman23 is prepping a take on the Air Jordan 1 Low reminiscent of the @diamondsupplyco x @nike Dunk Low “Tiffany.” Dubbed “Tropical Twist,” this iteration carries the same two-tone look found on the 2005 release and features a teal leather base accented by black overlays and a matching nylon tongue. Branding comes in the form of gradient Swooshes, color-matched tongue tags, printed insoles, and tonal black embroidered Wings motifs at the rear. Stay tuned for official release details.⁠⠀
Photo: Nike,@realcoleworld and @puma have officially announced the DREAMER 2 hoops shoe. Coming in an inaugural “January 28” colorway, the model features abstractly shaped overlays with a blend of leather, suede and synthetic materials in a louder yellow hue. The bottom sole unit is coated with black, while hits of red make its way onto the pods on the outsoles. Expect it to be available via PUMA’s NYC Flagship Store, website, and select stockists worldwide on January 28 for $135 USD.⁠⠀
Photo: PUMA

Bio: Past Present Future
Caption text: @goatsneakers: The Women’s Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘Starfish’ updates the classic silhouette, taking inspiration from the material and build of an astronaut’s space suit. Black metallic mesh covers the upper, contrasted by Starfish orange underlays that stand out via the sneaker’s raw-edge construction. Matte black distinguishes the TPU wings and heel tab, while an exposed-foam tongue offer a unique look. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Chicago-based retailer Notre works with Vans on a capsule collection inspired by community and togetherness. Four distinct Old Skool LX colors arrive with rich suede uppers, with an off-white vulcanized midsole and white laces. Jazz Stripes on the lateral sides are reworked with the Notre Handshake graphic, showcasing their mantra as a shop: teamwork, learning from one another, and staying open-minded. Available on the app and GOAT.com,The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Dark Mocha’ features rich earth tone hues, perfectly contrasting white, black and brown onto a classic silhouette. White leather base panels merge with black leather on the toe and Swoosh, while the heel and ankle area features Dark Mocha nubuck. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Not your traditional workwear. Classic silhouettes reimagined in unexpected textures, weights and patterns from the revolutionary new label and platform @MCQ. Discover the full FOAM collection, exclusively on GOAT.,@goatsneakers: The Nike Women’s Dunk Low ‘Coast’ highlights traditional two-tone color blocking on a leather upper that maintains the look of the original 1985 release. A crisp white base, replete with perforated detailing on the toe box, is contrasted by overlays in a vibrant ‘Coast’ blue finish. Nike branding on the heel tab and woven tongue tag arrive in University Gold for a nice color contrast. Available on the app and GOAT.com,The Nike Dunk High SB ‘MF DOOM’ embraces the late and legendary underground rapper with intricate details and artwork. The upper consists of black suede with Midnight Fog leather overlays and a faux ostrich skin toe area, accented with reflective piping. An MF Doom mask graphic adorns the tongue tags, while ‘Doom’ embroidery appears on the collar. Red laces offer a bold contrast, anchored by ‘SPR’ and ‘VLN’ lace dubraes while MF Doom artwork graces the sockliner and outsole.,@goatsneakers: Paris-based creative agency Studio FY7 teamed up with New Balance on the classic 992 silhouette. Celebrating studio founder Younes Bendjima’s native Algeria, this ‘Cream’ colorway features a rich suede upper inspired by the country’s sandy dunes, while contrasting black mesh circles give a nod to ancient architecture. It all rides on a split black and white ABZORB midsole, offering lightweight cushioning and a smooth ride. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Cozy, cooler. Shop hoodies and more cold-weather layering essentials, now on the app and GOAT.com,Air Jordans are not simply sneakers. They’re airborne icons that capture sport, innovation and art at their highest heights. From the groundbreaking Air Jordan 1 to the grand closing Air Jordan 14, discover the moments that defined one of the most iconic sneakers of all time. 🐲 4K digital restorations of The Big Boss, Fist of Fury, Game of Death, and The Way of the Dragon, with uncompressed original monaural soundtracks
• New 2K digital restoration of the rarely-seen 99-minute 1973 theatrical version of Enter the Dragon, with uncompressed original monaural soundtrack
• New 2K digital restoration of the 102-minute “special-edition” version of Enter the Dragon
Alternate audio soundtracks for the films, including original English-dubbed tracks and a 5.1 surround soundtrack for the special-edition version of Enter the Dragon
• Six audio commentaries: on The Big Boss by Bruce Lee expert Brandon Bentley; on The Big Boss, Fist of Fury, Game of Death, and The Way of the Dragon by Hong Kong–film expert Mike Leeder; and on the special-edition version of Enter the Dragon by producer Paul Heller
• High-definition presentation of Game of Death II, the 1981 sequel to Game of Death

• New interview with author Grady Hendrix about the “Bruceploitation” subgenre that followed Lee’s death, and a selection of Bruceploitation trailers
• Blood and Steel, a 2004 documentary about the making of Enter the Dragon
• Multiple programs and documentaries about Lee’s life and philosophies, including Bruce Lee: The Man and the Legend (1973) and Bruce Lee: In His Own Words (1998)
• Interviews with Linda Lee Cadwell, Lee’s widow, and many of Lee’s collaborators and admirers, including actors Jon T. Benn, Riki Hashimoto, Nora Miao, Robert Wall, Yuen Wah, and Simon Yam and directors Clarence Fok, Sammo Hung, and Wong Jing

🌊 @therealshannonlee flows with @kerrileewalsh.  Kerri Lee Walsh Jennings is the most decorated Olympic beach volleyball player of all time, with 3 gold medals and one bronze. She is the beach volleyball career leader in both victories and winnings and at age 41 is making her run up to another Olympics in Tokyo this summer and aiming for a fourth gold medal.  Kerri is married to beach volleyball player Casey Jennings and together they have three children. In fact, she competed while pregnant in the Olympics twice! Kerri and Casey launched their company @p1440 in 2018, a digital sports platform created to inspire everyone to live 1440 minutes of every day with purpose.

Kerri is an ardent Bruce Lee fan as you will come to see when you listen to this episode. With Kerri, her energy leaps out at you. She is a fast paced, energetic woman who channels Bruce Lee (and two other icons) on the court. [And you’ll want to find out which other 2 icons because it was pretty fascinating to me.] Kerri admits her fallibility and knows she is still learning and growing everyday as she continues to train and shoot for Olympic gold! She is a driven, passionate woman who is dedicated to her sport, her family and her faith. She is truly a go-getter who finds grounding in gratitude.  Kerri has a wealth of information and learnings to share as she seeks to grow and retain champion athlete status. Come get in on the mind of an athlete with Kerri Walsh Jennings.

Caption text:
😍 ¡La Copa que espera en el @maracana por su nuevo dueño! 

🔜 Falta una semana, sólo una semana para una #FinalDeOtroMundo en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores entre @palmeiras y @santosfc.

#GloriaEterna,⚽️😉 Gabigol, Pratto, Luan, Borja, Funes Mori, Ortigoza, Silva, Emerson, Neymar y Giuliano... ¿qué celebración te gustó más en la final de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores?

#GloriaEterna,⚽️🇧🇷 El delantero de 1⃣8⃣ años es una de las figuras del Peixe: suma 5⃣ goles en 1⃣1⃣ partidos en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔜🏆 El 30/1 jugará en el Maracaná su primera final en busca de la #GloriaEterna.

#Santos #SantosFC #KaioJorge,💪⚪️⚫️ ¡Lucas Veríssimo, uno de los pilares de la defensa de @santosfc que busca la @gloriaeterna! 

🏆 Fue él quien hizo el primer gol del #Peixe en Vila Belmiro en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores 2020.

🔜 ¡Faltan 8⃣ dias para la #FinalDeOtroMundo!,🇧🇷⚽️ En 1⃣1⃣ minutos, el Verdão marcó 3⃣ goles para sellar la serie de los Octavos de Final frente a #Delfín en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🏆 Llega a la Final como el segundo equipo más goleador: tiene 3⃣2⃣ festejos en 1⃣2⃣ encuentros.

#Palmeiras #PalmeirasSE #Verdão,🇻🇪⚽🗺¡De Venezuela en busca de la @gloriaeterna! 

🤍🖤 @yefersonsoteldo1006, con sólo 2⃣3⃣ años, es figura de @santosfc y busca la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔥⚽ Marcó dos goles en la Copa: en Octavos y en la Semifinal. 🤔 ¿Podrá convertir ante @palmeiras en el @maracana?,🥳¡Feliz cumpleaños, Rogério Ceni!

🏆Campeón de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores con @saopaulofc, una leyenda de la Copa festeja hoy 48 años. 

#GloriaEterna,🚫🖐️ Armani, Andrada, Azcona, Torrico, Víctor, Silva, Cássio, Sosa y Michel... ¿quién sacó la pelota más difícil en la definición de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores?

#GloriaEterna,⚽️🏆 El arquero brasilero suma 7⃣ vallas invictas y 3⃣9⃣ atajadas y solo recibió 6⃣ goles en 1⃣2⃣ partidos de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔜 ¿Será figura en la final frente a @santosfc para alcanzar la #GloriaEterna?

#Palmeiras #PalmeirasSE #Weverton,⚽️🇳🇬 ¡El dueño de la pelota! @luizadrianinho es el máximo anotador de @palmeiras en la temporada, con 2⃣0⃣ goles. Sus números en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores:

✅5⃣ goles
✅6⃣ partidos
✅1⃣1⃣ remates

🔜🏆 Faltan 9⃣ días para la #FinalDeOtroMundo: por la @GloriaEterna en el @maracana.

Bio:
Candidat a la presidència del F.C.Barcelona. Perquè Estimo el Barça! @estimemelbarca
Pàgina Oficial | Official Page
Caption text:
Treballarem de valent per tornar a ser competitius. Ho farem amb esperit d'equip, amb persones que senten els colors i amb la voluntat de tornar a ser ‘Més que un Club’. Ho farem realitat, culers.,#EstimemElBarça,Desitjo el millor avui als jugadors del Barça, que el Club guanyi la Supercopa, i que aquest sigui el primer títol, però no l’últim de la temporada. I espero les eleccions amb moltes ganes per servir al Barça i revertir la situació. Visca el Barça!!,Gràcies a la @penyabvaldivia i a la seva impulsora, Flor Andino, per l’acollida que ens han donat avui. Seguim explicant les nostres propostes a culers d'arreu i donant a conèixer el nostre projecte #EstimemElBarça. 
Seguim!,Les eleccions es preveuen el 7 de març. El Barça no pot estar més temps sense President ni Junta Directiva. Nosaltres seguirem preparats. Treballant incansablement per al Club i els i les sòcies. Una vegada més gràcies pel suport, aconseguirem revertir la situació, n’estic segur.,Oficialment sóc candidat a la presidència del Barça! Gràcies per estimar el Barça i gràcies pel suport que m’heu donat, us estic molt agraït! Ara necessito que el 24-G em voteu per ser president. Estic més convençut que mai que tornarem a reflotar el Barça! 💙❤️#EstimemElBarça,Avui hem presentat el nostre Pla Econòmic d'Acció per reactivar l'economia del Barça, un aspecte fonamental per la sostenibilitat del club i garantir el model de propietat actual.

Gràcies, Joan Casas, Jaume Giró i Alex Barbany pel vostre rigorós anàlisi i per les propostes innovadores que estic segur que seran clau per reflotar el club.,Gràcies a vosaltres seré candidat. I ja només faltarà un pas més per ser President del Barça! 10.257 gràcies, socis i sòcies!,Orgullós que barcelonistes que han format part del club confiïn en el nostre projecte. Gràcies per ser-hi Gabri García, Jesús Angoy, Txema Corbella i Gabi Cairo.

 Un plaer rebre-us a la casa d'@estimemelbarca i comptar amb el vostre suport!,Gràcies pel teu suport, @neusmunte! I l’Antonio Martínez de la @penyajohan! Sumar el suport de persones com vosaltres ens omple d’orgull. #EstimemElBarça

Bio:
The global destination for authentic sneakers.⠀
Download the app or visit GOAT.com
Caption text: The Bodega x Nike Dunk High ‘Friends & Family’ utilizes the same inspiration of Americana and old-world craftsmanship as the regular ‘Legend’ iteration, but arrives in a clean Sail and Birch colorway. Never released to the general public and given to friends and family of the Boston-based brand, consumers did have a shot at getting these if they purchased the ‘Legend’ colorway. Randomly inserting a pack of sports cards into 1 out of every 20 boxes, consumers who were lucky enough to find the cards could claim one of these F&F pairs. Available on the app and GOAT.com,The Social Status x Ultra 4D ‘Renaissance’ blends a futuristic sneaker with historical inspiration. Utilizing colors and tones inspired from Renaissance art, specifically da Vinci’s ‘Mona Lisa,’ the Ultra 4D features bold colors across a Primeknit upper and suede cage. A 3-D printed midsole offers customized cushioning, while a gum rubber outsole and Social Status and adidas co-branding finish the look. Limited to only 3,020 pairs, shop them on the app and GOAT.com,The Nike women’s Lahar Low ‘Wheat’ delivers a contemporary interpretation of the Lahar Escape Boot from 1989, featuring a dark tan suede upper secured with rope laces and metal eyelets. An Air sole unit in the heel offers lightweight cushioning while an off-road traction pattern on the thick outsole provides maximum grip. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Paying homage to the original silhouette, the Nike Air Max 95 NDSTRKT ‘Neon’ updates the lifestyle runner with a durable build. Keeping a similar but updated design, reflective neon webbing straps integrate into a mesh upper reinforced with rubberized overlays and a molded TPU cage. The midsole maintains the look of the original Air Max 95, highlighted by visible Nike Air cushioning in the heel and forefoot. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Part of a festive capsule collection that included the New Balance 992, the ‘Kithmas Collection’ saw Ronnie Fieg work on three colors of the classic running style. The ‘Team Red’ and ‘Burgundy Reef’ arrive with plush suede on the uppers, accented with mesh and leather detailing. A sculpted midsole features ABZORB technology for impact cushioning and dual branding finishes the look including KITH on the tongue and FIEG on the back heel. Available on the app and GOAT.com,A celebration of two high profile Nike athletes — LeBron James and Kylian Mbappé —results in unique iterations of the Nike Mercurial Superfly 7 and LeBron 18. The LeBron 18 ‘The Chosen 2’ features iridescent detailing across a black Knitposite 2.0 upper and a translucent outsole. The athletes’ inspiration can be seen throughout the shoe, including a basketball x football graphic and Chosen Two ambigram on the sockliners. Available on the app and GOAT.com,The Nike Dunk Low SP ‘UNLV’ revives one of the original colorways of the 1985 ‘Be True to Your School’ series, but in a low cut format versus the original high-top. The upper utilizes the team colors of the University of Las Vegas, highlighted by a neutral grey leather base with University Red overlays and a contrasting white midsole. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Designed by the Guangzhou artist, the Jason Deng x Nike Dunk Low Pro SB ‘Street Hawker’ pays homage to Chinese street food vendors and Chinese food culture at large. The uppers are covered in unique materials, colors, and Deng’s watercolor graphics, with individual details representing six regional dishes from six Chinese cities. They’re joined by additional cuisine-inspired flourishes, including a wood-grain Swoosh that nods to chopsticks, a blue-tinged sockliner representing porcelain bowls, and a coppery toe box standing in for boiling chili oil. ‘Food’ is spelled out in embroidered Chinese calligraphy on the back heel tab. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Ronnie Fieg and ASICS embarked on an ambitious project to celebrate the 30th anniversary of the Gel Lyte 3. ‘The Palette’ offers up thirty different iterations of the classic runner, crafted with premium suede in a tonal look. The colors were derived from KITH products throughout the brand’s history, inspiring thirty unique pairs including this ‘Dusty Mauve’ colorway. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Part of a capsule collection with the Tokyo-based fashion label, the AMBUSH x Nike Dunk High ‘Black’ applies a clean two-tone color scheme to the classic lifestyle silhouette. Inspired by Japanese bike, car and truck culture, an exaggerated Swoosh extends past the back of the shoe to convey a dynamic sense of movement while AMBUSH branding can be found on the TPU heel counter and on the tongue tag. Available on the app and GOAT.com

O Esporte Interativo agora é TNT Sports! Continue seguindo a gente na @tntsportsbr

Essa é a nova marca de esportes da WarnerMedia e será a integração da produção de conteúdo na América Latina. Com a mudança, todas as mídias e plataformas digitais que o Esporte Interativo está presente passam a estar com novo nome: @tntsportsbr. A linguagem, a qualidade do conteúdo produzido e a interação com o fã seguem no dia-a-dia e passam a romper fronteiras do Brasil.

Tanto no dia-a-dia nas principais notícias e assuntos, quanto na transmissão do Brasileirão, UEFA Champions League, Nations League, Campeonato Italiano... Além do Último Lance, Melhor da Liga, Liga Espetacular e De Olho na Liga.

E claro, no mundo dos games com o @eigames e na zoação do @desolaoficial!

Bio: "Women, with their intuitive instinct, understood that I dreamed not only of making them more beautiful, but happier too." Christian Dior
Caption text:
Enriching the proceedings with jolts of color, 'Dior and Peter Doig' camo print and refined embellishment, the ballet dancer @GuillaumeDiop, actor and musician @LukasIonesco and artist @KailandMorris caught yesterday's #DiorWinter21 digital show from @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig wearing looks from the collection itself.
© @Thomas_Chene,With #DiorWinter21 from @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig having been unveiled digitally yesterday, director @LadjLy and actors @ArnaudValois and @JLaheurte - wearing statement outerwear including a 'Dior and Peter Doig' print bomber jacket - were among the House friends from around the world discovering the new collection.
© @Thomas_Chene,Relive the finale of yesterday’s unveiling of #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in collaboration with the artist @PeterDoig. The closing look, featuring a plush shearling coat with a long, officer-style jacket, distills the spirit of the collection which explores the codes of ceremonial costume in a couture-informed, contemporary take on timeless masculine elegance.,The expressive brushwork of collaborative artist @PeterDoig daubs the modesty-maintaining panels on the front of a pair of sheer shirts for #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones, illuminating the celebrated painter's process as well as his finished works.,The enigmatic allure of the paintings of collaborative artist @PeterDoig unfolds both boldly and hazily across a number of standout coats from #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones. These hypnotic 'Dior and Peter Doig' prints are derived from emblematic works by the internationally celebrated painter including 'Milky Way' (1990).,The air of masculine majesty conveyed by ceremonial garb is explored and modernized for #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in collaboration with the artist @PeterDoig. The precision tailoring of officer jackets with their piping, braid and decorative buttons is mixed, in an inventive use of #DiorSavoirFaire, with embroideries possessing a more couture sensibility and tamed with the addition of colorful sportswear pieces, honoring history and heritage in a resolutely contemporary way.,See the show set from the recently-revealed #DiorWinter21 collection in which the collaboration between @MrKimJones and the artist @PeterDoig extended to an installation devised by the latter with blue skies and stacked sound systems that reference those in such paintings of his as 'Speaker/Girl' (2015). 
© Photo: @AdrienDirand,Knitwear provides a metaphorical canvas for animalistic imagery in the #DiorWinter21 collection by @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig. The latter specially conceived two motifs - one that's a likeness of Monsieur Dior's beloved dog, Bobby, and the other a lion that references the artist's own output - both rendered with a blurred effect that mimics the painter's style, further alluded to in an evocation of brushstrokes on another sweater.,Sample some of the highlights of the just-unveiled #DiorWinter21 collection by @MrKimJones created in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig. Channeling the latter’s oeuvre, whether indirectly through his color palette or directly through motifs drawn from his paintings, the collection draws inspiration from the timeless masculine elegance of ceremonial costume as viewed through a contemporary prism rooted in #DiorSavoirFaire.,Whether as layered looks in lustrous ‘Dior and Peter Doig’ camo prints or abstracted cashmere knits, the timeless military motif was reinterpreted in hues ranging from dusky to eye-popping in the just-ended showing of #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in a nod to the palette associated with the collection’s collaborative artist @PeterDoig.

Caption text:
Yessss!!!!
3️⃣ puntos más que viajan a Madrid. 
Orgulloso del trabajo del equipo hasta el último minuto. 
¡Enhorabuena, pistolero @luissuarez9 !
#AúpaAtleti,¡Vaaaaaamooooooos! 3 puntos y portería a 0. 💪❄️
#AúpaAtleti 🔴⚪,En cualquier momento entra bien @miwirealdrinks 😏🤪🥶,Por fin existe un refresco saludable y no me puede hacer más ilusión formar parte 💚♻️.

Os presento @miwirealdrinks , la primera marca de kombucha fabricada en España sin azúcares ✅. 
Ahora vais a poder disfrutar de un refresco además de cuidar vuestra salud y el planeta 🥤😍🌍.

Espero que os guste tanto como a mí y que veáis que, con iniciativas así, cuidarse no significa renunciar a nada🔝.,Otra victoria importante y trabajada. Y otro gol para ayudar al equipo 😉🤞🏻. 
Suerte al @deportivoalaves , siempre es bonito venir a este campo, siempre agradecido. 
#AúpaAtleti,Con esta foto empiezan mis recuerdos de 2020. Hoy el año termina y ya nada será igual. Además de acordarnos de quienes se nos han ido y de ser más conscientes que nunca de que la salud es lo primero, este año tan difícil nos deja también muchos aprendizajes. A mí, 2020 me demostró que lo conocido no siempre es mejor que lo que queda por conocer; que el cómo y el porqué siempre son más importantes que el dónde y el cuánto; y que el trabajo duro y la conciencia tranquila son la causa y la consecuencia de una forma de entender la vida y el mundo. 2021, vamos a por ti. Gracias a todos y muchas gracias por vuestro apoyo y cariño,Trabajo, trabajo, trabajo 💪🏻⚽️
#AúpaAtleti 🔴⚪️,Ronnie, Marqués, KD, @paddy.8 y yo os deseamos FELICES FIESTAS A TODOS. 🎄❤️🐶🐶🐶,➕3️⃣ y ⚽. Noche perfecta. ¡Vamos! 💪😁🔴⚪ #AúpaAtleti

Bio: Perfil oficial de Arturo Vidal, jugador del  @inter 🇮🇹 y de la Selección Chilena de Fútbol.
Caption text:
Ready, pronti,listos!!! 💪🏽🔥👑😉
Forza @inter 🖤💙 mañana con todo carajo, a seguir por el mismo camino!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽,Muchas Gracias por este lindo vídeo!!!❤️❤️ 👑💪🏽👍🏽😉,👑🤴🏽👑🤴🏽👑,La mia intenzione non è mai stata quella di baciare lo stemma di un altra squadra. Il bacio è stata una dimostrazione di affetto per un fratello che mi ha dato il calcio, con il quale ho vissuto anni meravigliosi insieme e ci vogliamo bene. 
Io rispetto la mia squadra, i nostri tifosi e la gente che ha avuto fiducia in me per difendere e continuare a far crescere la storia di questo bellissimo club. E lascerò l anima per quello! 
Forza @inter !!!🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙,💪🏽🔥 👑 💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Es una pena muy grande esta noticia de que no seguirá trabajando junto a nosotros en este camino al mundial. Se entiende y se respeta, principalmente por la responsabilidad de gente que hace daño al fútbol, como muchos de la prensa mediocre y algunos dirigentes que no entienden nada de nuestra actividad😡 .
Lo quiero mucho, le agradezco infinitamente y le deseo lo mejor a usted y a su cuerpo técnico en el camino que tomen 😢 , gracias por todo este tiempo juntos, por ayudarnos, todo lo que hagamos de acá en adelante también será por y para ustedes. 
Siempre fue un caballero con nosotros,un hombre valiente que tomó el desafío de acompañarnos en un momento difícil y nos ayudó a encontrar las fuerzas para seguir luchando por nuestra querida selección... GRACIAS PROFE ❤️ 🙏🏻
Le deseo lo mejor y nos vemos en Qatar 2022!!! 🇨🇴 🔥 🇨🇱 💪🏽💪🏽,Feliz por el paso a cuartos de copa y por mi primer gol, ahora vendrán muchas más forza @inter 🖤💙💪🏽👑🔥⚽️😉,🔥💪🏽👑 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Mal resultado por cómo se jugó!!😡 pero debemos seguir peleando y trabajando... aun queda mucho!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Pronto per domani 💪🏽Forza @inter 🖤💙 👑💪🏽 🔥 😉👍🏽 ⚽️

Bio:
Candidat a la presidència del F.C.Barcelona. Perquè Estimo el Barça! @estimemelbarca
Pàgina Oficial | Official Page
Caption text:
Treballarem de valent per tornar a ser competitius. Ho farem amb esperit d'equip, amb persones que senten els colors i amb la voluntat de tornar a ser ‘Més que un Club’. Ho farem realitat, culers.,#EstimemElBarça,Desitjo el millor avui als jugadors del Barça, que el Club guanyi la Supercopa, i que aquest sigui el primer títol, però no l’últim de la temporada. I espero les eleccions amb moltes ganes per servir al Barça i revertir la situació. Visca el Barça!!,Gràcies a la @penyabvaldivia i a la seva impulsora, Flor Andino, per l’acollida que ens han donat avui. Seguim explicant les nostres propostes a culers d'arreu i donant a conèixer el nostre projecte #EstimemElBarça. 
Seguim!,Les eleccions es preveuen el 7 de març. El Barça no pot estar més temps sense President ni Junta Directiva. Nosaltres seguirem preparats. Treballant incansablement per al Club i els i les sòcies. Una vegada més gràcies pel suport, aconseguirem revertir la situació, n’estic segur.,Oficialment sóc candidat a la presidència del Barça! Gràcies per estimar el Barça i gràcies pel suport que m’heu donat, us estic molt agraït! Ara necessito que el 24-G em voteu per ser president. Estic més convençut que mai que tornarem a reflotar el Barça! 💙❤️#EstimemElBarça,Avui hem presentat el nostre Pla Econòmic d'Acció per reactivar l'economia del Barça, un aspecte fonamental per la sostenibilitat del club i garantir el model de propietat actual.

Gràcies, Joan Casas, Jaume Giró i Alex Barbany pel vostre rigorós anàlisi i per les propostes innovadores que estic segur que seran clau per reflotar el club.,Gràcies a vosaltres seré candidat. I ja només faltarà un pas més per ser President del Barça! 10.257 gràcies, socis i sòcies!,Orgullós que barcelonistes que han format part del club confiïn en el nostre projecte. Gràcies per ser-hi Gabri García, Jesús Angoy, Txema Corbella i Gabi Cairo.

 Un plaer rebre-us a la casa d'@estimemelbarca i comptar amb el vostre suport!,Gràcies pel teu suport, @neusmunte! I l’Antonio Martínez de la @penyajohan! Sumar el suport de persones com vosaltres ens omple d’orgull. #EstimemElBarça

#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #hautehorology #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #inspiredbytheimpossible,Travel Back in Time. The Jacob & Co. Epic SF24 is a classic piece that incorporates a patented “Split Flap” technology that derives from the mechanical information boards that were once in airports and train stations all over the world.

.⠀

#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,Inspired by vintage Split Flap boards found in airports and train stations, the Epic SF24 managed to take this complicated idea and put it into a wristwatch. ⠀

.⠀
.⠀
.⠀

.⠀

#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #hautehorology #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #inspiredbytheimpossible,💎 Launching 💎 

It’s a Mystery. The Mystery Tourbillon Blue Camo combines the most intricate gem-setting yet with an incredibly complicated mechanism. The two disks that show the time are set in an overlapping fashion with baguette-cut hexagonal sapphires in various shades of blue, with one white diamond to indicate the time. This all leads to the middle of the timepiece, which showcases the mechanical ballet of the two triple-axis tourbillons, placed back-to-back and turning together.

.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,💎 New Launch 💎 

Marvelous Mystery. Sourcing the many different hues of blue sapphires for the Mystery Tourbillon Blue Camo took many months, then setting them involves one expert gem-setter for months. The two triple-axis tourbillons turn as one in the very center of the timepiece. The blue sapphire-set Mystery disks show the time by virtue of the single white diamond on each disk. All of this is protected by a domed sapphire crystal, putting everything on display.

.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
.⠀
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,💎 New Timepiece 💎 

Modern Mystery. Mystery clocks and watches have been around the watchmaking industry for more than a century. With the Mystery Tourbillon Blue Camo, Jacob & Co. brings the mystery concept into the 21st century. Rather than hands to indicate the time, the Mystery Tourbillon Blue Camo uses two blue sapphire-set disks, with one single white diamond on each disk to show the time. In the center of the watch are two triple-axis tourbillons, placed back-to-back, turning as one.

.⠀

.⠀
.⠀
.⠀

.⠀
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #luxurylifestyle #luxurywatches #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,Solar Splendor. Designed to be a solar system on the wrist, the Astronomia Solar features elements turning both clockwise and counterclockwise, while a 288-facet, Jacob-cut yellow sapphire sits on top of the high-watchmaking movement. The three satellite arms turn around the dial clockwise in 10 minutes, while the base dial set with white diamonds and red rubies turns counterclockwise in 10 minutes.

.
.
.
.
.
.
.
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,Rubies and Diamonds. The Astronomia Solar 3D Baguette combines the royal red of rubies with the brilliant sparkle of white diamonds while astounding with its high-watchmaking, double-axis tourbillon movement.

.
.
.
.
.
.
.
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,One-of-a-Kind. The Astronomia Solar 3D Baguette is a unique piece, one of one, that uses the Astronomia Solar movement, with elements moving clockwise and counterclockwise. Sitting on top of the everything is a 288-facet Jacob-cut Yellow Sapphire, representing our sun. The 45mm palladium case is set with white diamonds, while the base dial is set with white diamonds and red rubies.

.
.
.
.
.
.
.
#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #hautehorlogerie #hautehorology #inspiredbytheimpossible,The 47mm 18K white gold case, dial, buckle, lugs, and complete bracelet are invisibly set with 827 of the highest-quality white diamonds. The flying tourbillon is visible in an aperture at six o'clock, and the white diamond-set rear of the manual winding movement is visible through the exhibition case back.

Caption text:
South Korean label, @gort_shop has now delivered Drop 2 of its Fall/Winter 2020 collection. The assortment features relaxed styles led by bandana marked PATCHWORK REVERSIBLE QUILTING JACKETS inspired by traditional Korean Hanboks along with the extra warm FISHTAIL PARKA WITH LINER that reimagines the design of an M-65 jacket. GORT’s FW20 Drop 2 is now available at @432hz.official.⁠⠀
Photo: Gort/432hz,@dior's taps internationally renowned artist, @peterdoig for its upcoming Winter 2021 collection. The finely tailored range features Doig’s swirling brushstrokes translated into embroidered accents and knit sweaters. Printings of Doig’s Milky Way are found atop a peak lapel coat while shirting and various accessories are dressed in prints of lion figures. The vibrant imagery plays off the subverted militaristic codes, juxtaposing Doig’s gentle artwork against camouflaged anoraks and waistcoats. View all of Dior's Winter 2021 offerings by hitting the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Dior,@berniesanders has just released a crewneck design based on his viral pose at the recent Presidential Inauguration. The senator from Vermont has playfully responded with the launch of a simple black sweatshirt that plasters the comical image of himself across the front. Adding to the look is his personal “Bernie” logo printed on the lower right corner of the garment.⁠ The “Chairman Sanders” Crewneck is now available at the Bernie Campaign store for $45 USD, with all of the proceeds going towards Meals on Wheels Vermont.⁠
Photo: Bernie Campaign Store,@evisenskateco and @independenttrucks have teamed up for a concise graphic-filled capsule. The assortment includes a lineup of hoodies, anoraks, and graphic T-shirts. One standout piece is a multi-paneled anorak arriving in black, white, or olive. Co-branding from both labels is placed on the upper right sleeve over the anorak’s white panel, complete with twin waist pockets, and drawstrings at the hood. The collaboration will be available on January 23 on Evisen Skateboards’ website, ranging from ¥4,000 – ¥27,000 JPY (approximately $36 – $260 USD).⁠⠀
Photo: Evisen Skateboards,@fearofgod has now readied the introduction of its 2021 “Seventh Collection.” Included in the range is a celebration of the 100th-anniversary of the Negro Leagues. The tribute to the origins of baseball arrives in the form of a vintage baseball pullover jacket and henley tees featuring textured velvet flocking typography. Also included are elevated T-shirts, sweatshirts, and hoodies featuring a new iteration of the brand’s FG logo in a military-inspired stencil font. The “Seventh Collection” is set to drop in the coming week exclusively on the Fear of God website.
Photo: Fear of God,@carharttwip has revealed the lookbook for its Spring/Summer 2021 collection. The latest offering fuses the brand’s classic workwear and utilitarian influences with nods to the great outdoors and a selection of everyday staples. Workwear references vary from the continued use of robust canvas as a central material to the inclusion of new camouflage patterns. The collection's core everyday pieces range from triple stitch sweats to classic Single Knee Pants as well as graphic tees and hoodies. For a full look at the collection, hit the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Nicola Roman Walbeck,@steveaoki‘s @dimmakcollection and @playboy have teamed up for a special six-piece capsule. The limited pieces combine both Playboy and Dim Mak’s iconic branding and include two short sleeve t-shirts, two long-sleeve t-shirts, and two hoodies. The collection pays homage to Dim Mak Records’ founding year, with the number “96” featured in the graphics, while reflecting Aoki’s silhouette donning an Oni Menpo Samurai mask. The Playboy x Dim Mak collaboration collection is now available exclusively on @playboylabs.⁠⠀
Photo: Carter Jung & Josh "Midjordan" Farias,@driesvannoten is “dressing for our days” as seen through his Fall/Winter 2021 collection. Rife with rich textiles and flourishes, the range is cut looser than Van Noten’s previous efforts, blending elements of formality and sportswear in a relaxed hybrid that feels appropriate for endless days spent working from home. View more of the looks via the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Dries Van Noten,@elirusselllinnetz’s @erl__________ has envisioned an extensive assortment of playful garments rooted in Linnetz’s desire to create an effortless contemporary wardrobe for Fall/Winter 2021. Titled “The Final Frontier,” the range consists of signature pieces such as boxy hoodies, woven base layers, corduroy trousers that mingle with more progressive pieces, like metallic silver quilted outerwear and shearling-trimmed shirting. Get the full preview via the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: ERL,@asaprocky has showed off a new decorative set of grillz made with real flowers. Crafted by @grillzjewelz_is_right, the piece features a white gold base riddled with natural pink and canary yellow VVS diamonds for a striking top and bottom contrast look. Flowers have been suspended in a resin and embedded in two of the teeth, matching the colors of the surrounding stones. ⁠Swipe to get a closer look.⁠⠀
Photo: @jare.rah.mee/Tetsuya Akiyama

Bio: 🚀 🌎  Exploring the universe and our home planet.
Caption text:
A galaxy far, far away...50 million light-years from Earth, in the constellation of Virgo, the "lost galaxy" NGC 4535 shines, with its delicate swirls of newborn stars, burning furiously against their cool, blue ancestors.Despite the incredible quality of this image, taken from the NASA/ESA Hubble Space Telescope, NGC 4535 has a hazy, somewhat ghostly, appearance when viewed from a smaller telescope - inspiring its nickname, the “Lost Galaxy”.Credit: ESA/Hubble & NASA, J. Lee and the PHANGS-HST Team#NASA #Universe #Galaxy #Stars #Dreamy #Hubble #Virgo,Early evening sunlight dances down the valleys to warm the icy terrain.This natural-color Landsat 8 data was draped over a global digital elevation model of Greenland to create this unique view. The area lies a bit northeast of Gunnbjørn Fjeld, the tallest mountain in the country. The region is dotted with nunataks—rocky peaks that stick through glaciers and ice sheets—in the Watkins Range, Greenland’s tallest mountain range.Credit: NASA#Nasa #Greenland #MountainRange #Shadows #Light,🔵From Florida to Pluto to the Kuiper Belt and beyond!Exactly 15 years ago today, an uncrewed NASA spacecraft by the name of New Horizons blasted off on a 3 billion-mile journey to Pluto from Cape Canaveral Air Force Station by an @ULALaunch Atlas rocket at a speed of about 36,400 mph (16.26 km/s). It was the fastest human-made object EVER launched from Earth.By launching in 2006, New Horizons was able to take advantage of an assist from Jupiter. The Pluto probe approached a rendezvous with Jupiter and used the giant planet as a gravity-based slingshot. The five-month flyby induced a colossal burst of speed, accelerating the spacecraft by 9000 mph up to 52,000 mph. At that wild speed, you could soar from Los Angeles to New York in less than 4 minutes!After passing through the Pluto system in 2015, the spacecraft retargeted itself for an encounter with a Kuiper Belt Object (KBO) called Arrokoth, a Native American term meaning “sky” in the Powhatan/Agonquian language. While there, the spacecraft gathered data that researchers believe could contribute to our understanding of the origin of life on Earth.Credit: 🔵NASA🔵NASA/JHUAPL/SwRI🔵NASA/Johns Hopkins University Applied Physics Laboratory/Southwest Research Institute/Roman Tkachenko#NASA #Pluto #PlutoFlyBy #Space #Galaxy #Universe #Exploration,"Darkness cannot drive out darkness, only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate, only love can do that." — Dr. Martin Luther King Jr.⁣
⁣
Today we honor his legacy with this stunning image from space of Atlanta, #MLK's birthplace, alight amidst the dark of night.⁣
⁣
Credit: NASA⁣
⁣
#MLKDay #NASA #Space #Atlanta #CityLights #Love,How blue-tiful! 🤩🌌Near the outskirts of the Small Magellanic Cloud, a satellite galaxy about 200 thousand light-years away, lies this 5 million year young and dazzling star cluster known as NGC 602. Inside the star cluster, bright, blue, newly formed stars are blowing a cavity in this nebula, sculpting the inner edge of its outer portions, slowly eroding it away and eating into the material beyond. Star formation started at the center of the cluster and propagated outward, with the youngest stars still forming today along the dust ridges.Fun fact: Did you know that the color of a star is directly linked to its surface temperature? The hotter the star, the shorter the wavelength of light it will emit. The hottest of stars are blue or blue-white and the cooler ones are red or red-brown. What color star would you be?Credit: NASA#NASA #Stars #Universe #Galaxy #BlueStars #Astronomy #FunFacts,Get in loser, we're going stargazing 🌌Magnetic fields in Messier 82, or the Cigar galaxy, are shown here as lines over a visible light and infrared composite image of the galaxy from the @NASAHubble & the Spitzer Space Telescope. The galaxy located in the constellation Ursa Major is remarkable. Stellar winds streaming from hot new stars form a galactic super wind that blasts out plumes of hot gas (red) and a huge halo of smoky dust (yellow/orange) perpendicular to the narrow galaxy (white). Researchers used the Stratospheric Observatory for Infrared Astronomy (@sofiatelescope) magnetic field data and tools that have been used extensively to study the physics around the Sun to extrapolate the magnetic field’s strength 20,000 lights-years around the galaxy. The highways appear to extend indefinitely into intergalactic space, like the Sun’s solar wind, and may help explain how the gas and dust have traveled so far away from the galaxy. Credits: NASA, SOFIA, L. Proudfit; NASA, ESA, Hubble Heritage Team; NASA, JPL-Caltech, C. Engelbracht#NASA #M82 #Galaxy #Universe #Constellation #CigarGalaxy #UrsaMajor #SpaceHighway,In squad we trust 🚀Upside down or right side up? The seven-member Expedition 64 crew takes a moment to pose for a quick portrait inside the @ISS’ Kibo laboratory module from @jaxajp (Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency). Expedition 64 began in back in October 2020 with focused research investigations on biology, Earth science, human research, and more to provide the foundation for continuing human spaceflight beyond low-Earth orbit to the Moon and Mars!In the bottom row:NASA astronaut Kate Rubins@roscosmosofficial cosmonauts⭐ Sergey Ryzhikov⭐ Sergey Kud-SverchkovIn the top row:⭐ @jaxajp astronaut @astro.soichi@NASAAstronauts⭐ Michael Hopkins⭐ @AstroVicGlover⭐ Shannon WalkerGlover and Hopkins are wearing white uniforms that commemorate the NASA human spaceflight programs Mercury, Gemini, Apollo, Apollo-Soyuz, Space Shuttle, Shuttle-Mir, International Space Station and Commercial Crew.Credit: NASA#NASA #SquadGoals #Astronauts #Apollo #Expedition64 #Family #CommercialCrew #Science #STEM #Skywalkers,🤯 Discovery alert: We don’t know of many planets quite like this!Thanks to data from our @NASAGoddard TESS mission, a planet existing around THREE stars has been confirmed, after a hefty hunt that spanned about 11 years! It all started shortly after NASA's Kepler mission began operations in 2009, when it identified what was thought to be a planet about the size of Neptune later known as KOI-5Ab. The planet which was the second new planet candidate to be found by the mission, was ultimately forgotten as Kepler racked up planet discoveries. Now, the chief scientist of NASA’s Exoplanet Science Institute says he has “resurrected KOI-5Ab from the dead!" and we are so glad he did. Planet KOI-5Ab (shown here transiting across the face of a sun-like star), is located 1,800 light-years away in the Cygnus constellation. It is about one half the mass of Saturn & orbits a star (star A) with a relatively close companion (star B). Star A and star B orbit each other every 30 years. A third gravitationally bound star (star C) orbits stars A and B every 400 years.Illustration Credits: Caltech/R. Hurt (Infrared Processing and Analysis Center, or IPAC)#NASA #Galaxy #Universe #NewWorld #TripleStarSystem #NewDiscovery #LookUp #Space,It’s more than a feeling 🎵Much like the delicate filaments of a spider's web, the glowing lights of the city of Boston seemingly spread from a central point in this image taken by the crew of the @ISS as it orbited 263 miles above Earth's surface. What city would you want to look at if you were fluttering about in space on a Friday in January?Credit: NASA#NASA #Earth #Views #Galaxy #Universe #Boston #Massachusetts,Bon Voyage, #Cygnus! 🦾Yesterday, about three months after delivering nearly 8,000 pounds (3,628 kilograms) of scientific experiments, supplies, commercial products, hardware, and more to the @ISS, @NorthropGrumman’s uncrewed Cygnus cargo spacecraft departed the orbiting lab. Flight controllers on the ground sent commands to use the @CanadianSpaceAgency's Canadarm2 robotic arm to robotically detach Cygnus from the Earth-facing port of the unity module and maneuver it into place. Before the craft took off, the crew packed Cygnus with the Saffire V investigation & the SharkSat hosted payload to be conducted during an extended mission in orbit.  It'll complete a series of milestones to move away safely & remain in orbit until Jan. 26, for an extended mission with science experiments.Photo Credit: NASA#NASA #NorthropGrumman #USA #Canada #Robotics #Earth #ISS #CanadArm2

Bio: Perfil oficial de Arturo Vidal, jugador del  @inter 🇮🇹 y de la Selección Chilena de Fútbol.
Caption text:
Ready, pronti,listos!!! 💪🏽🔥👑😉
Forza @inter 🖤💙 mañana con todo carajo, a seguir por el mismo camino!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽,Muchas Gracias por este lindo vídeo!!!❤️❤️ 👑💪🏽👍🏽😉,👑🤴🏽👑🤴🏽👑,La mia intenzione non è mai stata quella di baciare lo stemma di un altra squadra. Il bacio è stata una dimostrazione di affetto per un fratello che mi ha dato il calcio, con il quale ho vissuto anni meravigliosi insieme e ci vogliamo bene. 
Io rispetto la mia squadra, i nostri tifosi e la gente che ha avuto fiducia in me per difendere e continuare a far crescere la storia di questo bellissimo club. E lascerò l anima per quello! 
Forza @inter !!!🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙,💪🏽🔥 👑 💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Es una pena muy grande esta noticia de que no seguirá trabajando junto a nosotros en este camino al mundial. Se entiende y se respeta, principalmente por la responsabilidad de gente que hace daño al fútbol, como muchos de la prensa mediocre y algunos dirigentes que no entienden nada de nuestra actividad😡 .
Lo quiero mucho, le agradezco infinitamente y le deseo lo mejor a usted y a su cuerpo técnico en el camino que tomen 😢 , gracias por todo este tiempo juntos, por ayudarnos, todo lo que hagamos de acá en adelante también será por y para ustedes. 
Siempre fue un caballero con nosotros,un hombre valiente que tomó el desafío de acompañarnos en un momento difícil y nos ayudó a encontrar las fuerzas para seguir luchando por nuestra querida selección... GRACIAS PROFE ❤️ 🙏🏻
Le deseo lo mejor y nos vemos en Qatar 2022!!! 🇨🇴 🔥 🇨🇱 💪🏽💪🏽,Feliz por el paso a cuartos de copa y por mi primer gol, ahora vendrán muchas más forza @inter 🖤💙💪🏽👑🔥⚽️😉,🔥💪🏽👑 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Mal resultado por cómo se jugó!!😡 pero debemos seguir peleando y trabajando... aun queda mucho!!!💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽 Forza @inter 🖤💙,Pronto per domani 💪🏽Forza @inter 🖤💙 👑💪🏽 🔥 😉👍🏽 ⚽️

Caption text:
Last week The Stig was sliding an Ariel Atom 4 about, so from one lightweight hero to another, here he is piloting an Alpine A110. At just a smidge over 1100kg, 248bhp is more than enough for sports car performance, but will it drift? Let's find out. Leave your drift rating in the comments below.

#alpine #alpinea110 #alpinea110s #renaultalpine #renaultalpinea110 #drift #drifting #driftcar  #motorsport #topgear #stigdrifts #thestig,More pics of Singer's awesome All-terrain Competition Study (ACS) - a co-developed project between Singer and British company Tuthill Porsche. 

Built at the request of a client who wanted an air-cooled 911 that could cope with the world’s most extreme off-road races, it pays homage to a golden era of Porsche rallying in the 1980s and to cars like the 959 Safari. 

It has four-wheel drive, a turbocharged flat-six, carbon panels, trick suspension and a stripped out interior, but still retains the outrageous attention to detail of all Singer’s creations. 

Here it is in action. Get the full story at TopGear.com. Link in bio. 

📸 @mark_scenemedia 

#topgear #singer #acs #porsche #dakar #rally #motorsport #carsofinstagram #carsofinsta,Ever wondered what goes on at the Top Gear test track when the show's not being filmed? Well it's this. Constant, non-stop THIS. Yep, Stig's got his hands on the latest 720bhp Merc-AMG Black Series and wants to bonfire some tyres. Enjoy...

#mercedes #mercedesamg #mercedesamggt #amggt #topgear #topgearmagazine #thestig,This is a serious car, for serious driving. We know this because no other production car has ever hammered around the Nordschleife faster than the AMG GT Black Series.

This is a consummate performer on the track. A road car that looks, acts and feels more like a GT3 racer than any other. If you want a car to fill you with confidence and make you feel every inch the hardcore racer, this new Black Series does it.

AMGs are traditionally engine-dominated, and this one has 150bhp more than the next model down the range. But by switching to a flat-plane crankshaft, the 4.0 twin-turbo V8 can now rev much higher and that allows the torque to be introduced more gently and sustained for longer. So it's got better traction. Unless...

Insert The Stig into the new Black Series and this most binary of not-quite-humans will revert to either his zero or one setting: flat-out or flat-out with lots of smoke. Clearly, The Stig believes a Black Series should be for one thing only. And it does do that one thing spectacularly well. Provided you are, in fact, The Stig. The rest of us mere mortals are going to find the Black Series somewhat harder to boss around...

Full video coming soon...

📸  @mark_scenemedia

#TopGear #TopGearMagazine #AutomativePhotography #CarPhotography #CarsofInstagram #CarsofInsta #MercedesAMG #BlackSeries #GTBlackSeries #TheStig,This is the all-new 'baby' Rolls-Royce - the Ghost. And with this new car, Rolls has gone in search of what it calls 'post opulence'. That's a more restrained aesthetic to you and I. Or put simply, anti-bling. But crucially, it's £250k of all-new engineering magnificence. So, pour yourself a glass of fizz, sit back, and find out why the new Ghost earned the coveted award for Top Gear's Luxury Car of the Year. 

#rolls #rollsroyce #TopGear #Ghost #RollsRoyceGhost #luxury #luxurycars #carsofinstagram #carsofinsta,The last 12 months have seen some cracking new additions and a few mid-life alterations to the hot hatch game. The already brilliant Civic Type R had an update with some special lightweight editions, VW released the 8th iteration of their benchmark for the sector – the Golf GTI – and then Toyota came along and blindsided everyone with the Toyota GR Yaris homologation special... But what should you buy? Here's our quick buying guide...

#toyotagryaris #gryaris #honda #CivicTypeR #TypeR #AMG #FiestaST #ford #hyundai #hyundaii30n #audi #S3,Meet the 1980s bike that fits into a tiny wee hot hatch.

The Motocompo is the smallest scooter Honda ever made. Which is no accident, because what you’re looking at is a bike designed specifically to fold up and squeeze into the boot of a car.

The car it was designed as an accessory to was also a tiddler, the City hatchback which is essentially an ancestor of today’s Jazz. Thus the ‘Compo had to be really small, and folded up, it’s 118cm by 54cm and sits held in place by a couple of simple harnesses in the back of the City II Turbo as snugly as a plastic toy inside a Kinder Egg.

Production lasted just two years, with sales between 1981 and ’83 just tipping over 50,000. But while it’s undeniably a cute solution to urban gridlock, the process of parking up your car and unfurling the bike it sheathes is far from elegant. The Motocompo may be little bigger than a holiday suitcase, but with a 49cc two-stroke and a fuel tank aboard, it’s significantly chunkier at about 45 kilos...

@stephendobie tries out the Honda Motocompo at TopGear.com. Link in bio. 

📸 @mark_scenemedia 

#TopGear #AutomotivePhotography #Honda #Motocompo #HondaMotocompo #Retrobikes #RetroScooters,Here’s a question - would you book a two week holiday off work, fly half way around the world with your wife and two kids in tow, just to see a Vauxhall?

Thought not. But that’s exactly what an Aussie family did at the Goodwood Festival of Speed, and you’re looking at the reason for that mammoth trip right here. She (and yes, ‘she’ is definitely the correct term) is called Baby Bertha.

Bertha hails from the mid-70s, a time when the wildly popular British club racing scene (think British Touring Cars at the height of their late 90s pomp), featured drivers with mutton chop sideburns and cars with cartoonish proportions. With a 0-100mph time of 7.8 seconds, she was 6.2 seconds faster than a contemporary Lamborghini Countach. Bertha was designed for one thing only: to win the Super Saloon championship.

Two seasons later and she’d won it twice on the bounce: box very much ticked. In her first year in 1975, she won 20 of the 24 races she entered. The following year it was 10 from 13, with two retirements and a second. That season also happened to include six lap records, all bar one of them with an average speed of over 100mph.

Worth travelling the world for? Head over to TopGear.com to find out why this legendary racer still pulls in the crowds. Link in bio.

📸  @jonnyfleetwood 

#TopGear #CarsofInsta #CarsofInstagram #AutomotivePhotography #CarPhotography #Bertha #BabyBertha #VauxhallFirenza,Yes, The Stig is back in one of Blighty's finest - the Ariel Atom 4. Now it's not the obvious choice for a drift wagon, we'll admit, but with the Atom 4's new torquier turbocharged engine, The Stig's feather-touch left-foot braking - oh, and 538bhp/tonne - let's see just how sideways it'll go. What would you rate this car control out of ten?

#topgear #thestig #stig #stigdrifts #carsofinstagram #carsofinsta #ariel #arielatom #atom4 #drifting #motorsport,#TopGear recently brought you news of Singer's new rally car, including some splendid images of it hurtling through the air at great speed. Impressive, no?

Anyway, that got us thinking. What cars have we captured in similarly, er, lofty, positions? So we went trawling through the archives, and decided it only fair to share some of our best shots with you. You know, like a two-tonne-plus Bentley Continental GT getting 'sick air'. We were just testing the staying power of the roof rack, honest...

Anyway, which of these gravity-defying cars would be top of your list for a test flight?

Check out the Singer ACS and see our full gallery of flying cars at TopGear.com. Links in bio.

set design c/o @l_aura_tocchet photography c/o @claudiazalla,On February 2, 2021, Off-White™ is set to reveal its combination of womenswear and menswear Spring/Summer 2021 collection through an all new digital experience.

Off-White’s founder and creative director Virgil Abloh hints: “Think personal connections through a public platform. Connecting the dots of distance through a global language. Linking up, even though we may be thousands of miles apart."

ICONS is now available online at off---white.com, canary---yellow.com, select Off-White™ boutiques worldwide and through SNKRS in North America. A wider release follows February 5 from taschen.com and global retailers.
——

"The ICONS book is, in a way, the only revealing lens to understand that the catalog of the 50-plus Nike shoes I have designed are in my mind “one shoe." One story." ~ @virgilabloh. 

——
ICONS, published by Taschen, is a dynamic retrospective of the extensive collaborative project between NIKE, Inc. and @virgilabloh.

Underpinned by The Ten, ICONS explores how the partnership works to unify all the intangible cultural threads connected to sneakers. The book traces Abloh’s investigative, creative process through documentation of prototypes, original text messages from Abloh to Nike designers and treasures from the Nike archives.

😍 ¡La Copa que espera en el @maracana por su nuevo dueño! 

🔜 Falta una semana, sólo una semana para una #FinalDeOtroMundo en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores entre @palmeiras y @santosfc.

#GloriaEterna,⚽️😉 Gabigol, Pratto, Luan, Borja, Funes Mori, Ortigoza, Silva, Emerson, Neymar y Giuliano... ¿qué celebración te gustó más en la final de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores?

#GloriaEterna,⚽️🇧🇷 El delantero de 1⃣8⃣ años es una de las figuras del Peixe: suma 5⃣ goles en 1⃣1⃣ partidos en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔜🏆 El 30/1 jugará en el Maracaná su primera final en busca de la #GloriaEterna.

#Santos #SantosFC #KaioJorge,💪⚪️⚫️ ¡Lucas Veríssimo, uno de los pilares de la defensa de @santosfc que busca la @gloriaeterna! 

🏆 Fue él quien hizo el primer gol del #Peixe en Vila Belmiro en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores 2020.

🔜 ¡Faltan 8⃣ dias para la #FinalDeOtroMundo!,🇧🇷⚽️ En 1⃣1⃣ minutos, el Verdão marcó 3⃣ goles para sellar la serie de los Octavos de Final frente a #Delfín en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🏆 Llega a la Final como el segundo equipo más goleador: tiene 3⃣2⃣ festejos en 1⃣2⃣ encuentros.

#Palmeiras #PalmeirasSE #Verdão,🇻🇪⚽🗺¡De Venezuela en busca de la @gloriaeterna! 

🤍🖤 @yefersonsoteldo1006, con sólo 2⃣3⃣ años, es figura de @santosfc y busca la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔥⚽ Marcó dos goles en la Copa: en Octavos y en la Semifinal. 🤔 ¿Podrá convertir ante @palmeiras en el @maracana?,🥳¡Feliz cumpleaños, Rogério Ceni!

🏆Campeón de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores con @saopaulofc, una leyenda de la Copa festeja hoy 48 años. 

#GloriaEterna,🚫🖐️ Armani, Andrada, Azcona, Torrico, Víctor, Silva, Cássio, Sosa y Michel... ¿quién sacó la pelota más difícil en la definición de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores?

#GloriaEterna,⚽️🏆 El arquero brasilero suma 7⃣ vallas invictas y 3⃣9⃣ atajadas y solo recibió 6⃣ goles en 1⃣2⃣ partidos de la CONMEBOL #Libertadores.

🔜 ¿Será figura en la final frente a @santosfc para alcanzar la #GloriaEterna?

#Palmeiras #PalmeirasSE #Weverton,⚽️🇳🇬 ¡El dueño de la pelota! @luizadrianinho es el máximo anotador de @palmeiras en la temporada, con 2⃣0⃣ goles. Sus números en la CONMEBOL #Libertadores:

✅5⃣ goles
✅6⃣ partidos
✅1⃣1⃣ remates

🔜🏆 Faltan 9⃣ días para la #FinalDeOtroMundo: por la @GloriaEterna en el @maracana.

Primeiro, minha mãe e, logo, meu pai - ambos venceram o covid19. Quero deixar meus mais sinceros agradecimentos ao Jeferson (diretor da Rede D’or de hospitais), ao Dr.Bruno do Copa Star, aos médicos, enfermeiras e toda a equipe pelo excelente atendimento aos meus pais. Foram dois meses de muita angústia! E, graças a Deus, deu tudo certo! Obrigado aos amigos e fãs que enviaram energia positiva! Se cuidem! Falta pouco, mas não podemos baixar a guarda! Deus abençoe a todos! 🙏🏽❤️,Um século de história! Parabéns @cruzeiro e muito obrigado por ter me projetado para o mundo! #cruzeirocentenario,Happy 2021!❤️💜❤️💜,Feliza natal!❤️💜,12 anos da minha princesa @ms__nazario 🍟🍔🎂❤️💜❤️,Alguns registros do #galaticosopen2020 pra agradecer a galera que participou, a brilhante e profissional organização da @givaldobarbosatennis e também do @luapaphac, além - claro - da clínica do @fsaretta. Muito obrigado!

Em quadra, nossos “atletas” nos surpreenderam pela qualidade e também pela dedicação a esse esporte incrível que é o tênis.

Parabéns aos vencedores @pauloandreofficial (que derrotou o craque @kaka na final) e @di6ao (vencedor da chave B sobre o @rnldmusic).

🐲 4K digital restorations of The Big Boss, Fist of Fury, Game of Death, and The Way of the Dragon, with uncompressed original monaural soundtracks
• New 2K digital restoration of the rarely-seen 99-minute 1973 theatrical version of Enter the Dragon, with uncompressed original monaural soundtrack
• New 2K digital restoration of the 102-minute “special-edition” version of Enter the Dragon
Alternate audio soundtracks for the films, including original English-dubbed tracks and a 5.1 surround soundtrack for the special-edition version of Enter the Dragon
• Six audio commentaries: on The Big Boss by Bruce Lee expert Brandon Bentley; on The Big Boss, Fist of Fury, Game of Death, and The Way of the Dragon by Hong Kong–film expert Mike Leeder; and on the special-edition version of Enter the Dragon by producer Paul Heller
• High-definition presentation of Game of Death II, the 1981 sequel to Game of Death
• Game of Death Redux, a new presentation of Lee’s original Game of Death footage, produced by Alan Canvan
• New interview with producer Andre Morgan about Golden Harvest, the company behind Hong Kong’s top martial-arts stars, including Lee
• New program about English-language dubbing with voice performers Michael Kaye (the English-speaking voice of Lee’s Chen Zhen in Fist of Fury) and Vaughan Savidge
• New interview with author Grady Hendrix about the “Bruceploitation” subgenre that followed Lee’s death, and a selection of Bruceploitation trailers
• Blood and Steel, a 2004 documentary about the making of Enter the Dragon
• Multiple programs and documentaries about Lee’s life and philosophies, including Bruce Lee: The Man and the Legend (1973) and Bruce Lee: In His Own Words (1998)
• Interviews with Linda Lee Cadwell, Lee’s widow, and many of Lee’s collaborators and admirers, including actors Jon T. Benn, Riki Hashimoto, Nora Miao, Robert Wall, Yuen Wah, and Simon Yam and directors Clarence Fok, Sammo Hung, and Wong Jing
• Promotional materials
• New English subtitle translations and subtitles for the deaf and hard of hearing,🐲🎙🎧 Bruce Lee Podcast Episode #213 of the Be Water 🌊 Season is LIVE —> Subscribe, Download and Listen: link in bio or go to www.brucelee.com/podcast, Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher + more.

🌊 @therealshannonlee flows with @kerrileewalsh.  Kerri Lee Walsh Jennings is the most decorated Olympic beach volleyball player of all time, with 3 gold medals and one bronze. She is the beach volleyball career leader in both victories and winnings and at age 41 is making her run up to another Olympics in Tokyo this summer and aiming for a fourth gold medal.  Kerri is married to beach volleyball player Casey Jennings and together they have three children. In fact, she competed while pregnant in the Olympics twice! Kerri and Casey launched their company @p1440 in 2018, a digital sports platform created to inspire everyone to live 1440 minutes of every day with purpose.

Kerri is an ardent Bruce Lee fan as you will come to see when you listen to this episode. With Kerri, her energy leaps out at you. She is a fast paced, energetic woman who channels Bruce Lee (and two other icons) on the court. [And you’ll want to find out which other 2 icons because it was pretty fascinating to me.] Kerri admits her fallibility and knows she is still learning and growing everyday as she continues to train and shoot for Olympic gold! She is a driven, passionate woman who is dedicated to her sport, her family and her faith. She is truly a go-getter who finds grounding in gratitude.  Kerri has a wealth of information and learnings to share as she seeks to grow and retain champion athlete status. Come get in on the mind of an athlete with Kerri Walsh Jennings.

📸 Erico Leonan / saopaulofc,🇾🇪🎂 Hoje o Rogério Ceni completa 48 anos de vida. A nossa história juntos, o carinho e o respeito são eternos. 

Parabéns, M1TO! 👏,🎥 Raí: “Estamos todos muito juntos para buscar essa recuperação”.,Dani Alves: “Quando os resultados estavam vindo, a responsabilidade era nossa. Agora que não estão vindo, também é nossa. Só nós podemos tirar o São Paulo desse momento. Se estamos no direito de pedir alguma coisa - porque acho que estamos mais no momento de oferecer do que de pedir -, pedimos que os torcedores não desistam da gente”.,O São Paulo eliminou o Palmeiras e avançou à decisão da Copa do Brasil Sub-17! O Tricolor conquistou a vaga nos pênaltis (5x4), em Cotia, após derrota por 2 a 0 no tempo normal - no primeiro jogo, triunfo são-paulino por 2 a 0, gols feitos Mateus Amaral e Patryck. Na decisão, os garotos #MadeInCotia vão enfrentar o Fluminense, com tabela a ser definida pela CBF.

#VamosSãoPaulo 🇾🇪

📸 Igor Amorim/saopaulofc.net,Juanfran: “Já tive muitas derrotas no futebol e na vida, piores do que essa. A gente vai se levantar, é o que esse clube merece. Estou completamente seguro que depois do jogo contra o Coritiba as coisas estarão diferentes. Vamos lutar até o fim, eu não vou me render.”,🇾🇪 O Tricolor está escalado! Their activities would not be merely permitted but actively facilitated. Their culture not stolen or misappropriated but fully celebrated and credited.”⁠

Bio: "Women, with their intuitive instinct, understood that I dreamed not only of making them more beautiful, but happier too." Christian Dior
Caption text:
Enriching the proceedings with jolts of color, 'Dior and Peter Doig' camo print and refined embellishment, the ballet dancer @GuillaumeDiop, actor and musician @LukasIonesco and artist @KailandMorris caught yesterday's #DiorWinter21 digital show from @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig wearing looks from the collection itself.
© @Thomas_Chene,With #DiorWinter21 from @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig having been unveiled digitally yesterday, director @LadjLy and actors @ArnaudValois and @JLaheurte - wearing statement outerwear including a 'Dior and Peter Doig' print bomber jacket - were among the House friends from around the world discovering the new collection.
© @Thomas_Chene,Relive the finale of yesterday’s unveiling of #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in collaboration with the artist @PeterDoig. The closing look, featuring a plush shearling coat with a long, officer-style jacket, distills the spirit of the collection which explores the codes of ceremonial costume in a couture-informed, contemporary take on timeless masculine elegance.,The expressive brushwork of collaborative artist @PeterDoig daubs the modesty-maintaining panels on the front of a pair of sheer shirts for #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones, illuminating the celebrated painter's process as well as his finished works.,The enigmatic allure of the paintings of collaborative artist @PeterDoig unfolds both boldly and hazily across a number of standout coats from #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones. These hypnotic 'Dior and Peter Doig' prints are derived from emblematic works by the internationally celebrated painter including 'Milky Way' (1990).,The air of masculine majesty conveyed by ceremonial garb is explored and modernized for #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in collaboration with the artist @PeterDoig. The precision tailoring of officer jackets with their piping, braid and decorative buttons is mixed, in an inventive use of #DiorSavoirFaire, with embroideries possessing a more couture sensibility and tamed with the addition of colorful sportswear pieces, honoring history and heritage in a resolutely contemporary way.,See the show set from the recently-revealed #DiorWinter21 collection in which the collaboration between @MrKimJones and the artist @PeterDoig extended to an installation devised by the latter with blue skies and stacked sound systems that reference those in such paintings of his as 'Speaker/Girl' (2015). 
© Photo: @AdrienDirand,Knitwear provides a metaphorical canvas for animalistic imagery in the #DiorWinter21 collection by @MrKimJones in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig. The latter specially conceived two motifs - one that's a likeness of Monsieur Dior's beloved dog, Bobby, and the other a lion that references the artist's own output - both rendered with a blurred effect that mimics the painter's style, further alluded to in an evocation of brushstrokes on another sweater.,Sample some of the highlights of the just-unveiled #DiorWinter21 collection by @MrKimJones created in collaboration with artist @PeterDoig. Channeling the latter’s oeuvre, whether indirectly through his color palette or directly through motifs drawn from his paintings, the collection draws inspiration from the timeless masculine elegance of ceremonial costume as viewed through a contemporary prism rooted in #DiorSavoirFaire.,Whether as layered looks in lustrous ‘Dior and Peter Doig’ camo prints or abstracted cashmere knits, the timeless military motif was reinterpreted in hues ranging from dusky to eye-popping in the just-ended showing of #DiorWinter21 by @MrKimJones in a nod to the palette associated with the collection’s collaborative artist @PeterDoig.

Vaccino anti Covid in Italia: quanti sono i vaccinati? Il report regione per regione
➖
I dati forniti dal Governo sulla campagna di vaccinazione contro il Covid. Il numero dei vaccinati alle 20.03 del 22 gennaio è di 1.312.275. Oltre 790mila gli operatori sanitari che hanno ricevuto il vaccino. In testa per percentuale di vaccinati rispetto alle dosi ricevute ci sono P.A. di Bolzano, Piemonte e Friuli Venezia Giulia. Le quantità consegnate sono calcolate considerando 5 dosi per fiala. Eventuali valori percentuali superiori a 100 evidenziano l’utilizzo della 6^ dose
➖

#SkySport #Covid19 #Coronavirus,PAPU GOMEZ-SIVIGLIA, AVANTI TUTTA: OPERAZIONE IN CHIUSURA CON L’ATALANTA
➖
Il Papu Gomez è pronto a lasciare la Serie A. Dopo le riflessioni delle scorse ore il Siviglia si è convinto a tentare l’affondo per l’argentino classe 1987 dell'Atalanta. Ci sono stati dei contatti e il ds spagnolo Monchi prepara il colpo potrebbe chiudere già a breve, offendo una cifra tra i 5 e i 6 milioni più bonus all'Atalanta. Resta da trovare un'intesa sui bonus, che saranno compresi tra uno e due milioni, ma la trattativa è molto avviata
➖
L'Atalanta è d'accordo con la cessione, avendo posto un veto sulla partenza del calciatore verso un club diretto concorrente in classifica in Serie A, mentre Gomez - a Bergamo dal 2014, con 252 presenze e 59 reti in nerazzurro - avrà la possibilità di continuare a giocare in Champions League. L'operazione potrebbe essere chiusa in poco tempo, forse già sabato
➖
