#SkySerieA #SerieA #SkySport #Benevento #Torino #Calcio #Football,MILAN-ATALANTA, PIOLI: "MANDZUKIC pronto per la convocazione. Può anche giocare con IBRAHIMOVIC"
➖
Cinque vittorie nelle ultime sei partite di campionato e primo posto ancora in mano. Il Milan continua a viaggiare spedito, e sabato alle 18 sfiderà l’Atalanta a San Siro. Alla vigilia della gara ha parlato Stefano Pioli in conferenza stampa: "Siamo consapevoli delle nostre qualità, e affrontare ogni gara con delle convinzioni è importante. Ma abbiamo anche grande rispetto degli avversari. L’Atalanta è una squadra forte, a cui non serve fare i complimenti. Stanno facendo un percorso fantastico e da due anni sono in Champions, hanno anche sfiorato la semifinale. Comunque noi proveremo a vincere. Serviranno lucidità e intensità, sarà una partita fisica". E sul nuovo acquisto, Mandzukic: "Si è inserito subito bene, ha già giocato in Serie A e ha una mentalità europea. Fisicamente sta molto bene, non gioca da tempo ma si è presentato in forma e determinato. Ci sono due ipotesi: o lo tengo fuori 3-4 settimane per trovare la condizione, o lo metto dentro per dargli ritmo. Scelgo quest’ultima opzione. Sta bene ed è pronto per essere convocato"
➖
"Mandzukic e Ibrahimovic insieme? Credo che sarà una possibilità. Nella mia visione e in quella dell'area tecnica, Mario può giocare insieme a Zlatan. Poi saranno le situazioni a determinare le scelte. Il ruolo di Mario? Ne ho parlato con lui, ha detto che gioca dove serve alla squadra per vincere. Vedremo man mano, quando crescerà la sua condizione"
➖

Caption text:
Yessss!!!!
3️⃣ puntos más que viajan a Madrid. 
Orgulloso del trabajo del equipo hasta el último minuto. 
¡Enhorabuena, pistolero @luissuarez9 !
#AúpaAtleti,¡Vaaaaaamooooooos! 3 puntos y portería a 0. 💪❄️
#AúpaAtleti 🔴⚪,En cualquier momento entra bien @miwirealdrinks 😏🤪🥶,Por fin existe un refresco saludable y no me puede hacer más ilusión formar parte 💚♻️.

Os presento @miwirealdrinks , la primera marca de kombucha fabricada en España sin azúcares ✅. 
Ahora vais a poder disfrutar de un refresco además de cuidar vuestra salud y el planeta 🥤😍🌍.

Espero que os guste tanto como a mí y que veáis que, con iniciativas así, cuidarse no significa renunciar a nada🔝.,Otra victoria importante y trabajada. Y otro gol para ayudar al equipo 😉🤞🏻. 
Suerte al @deportivoalaves , siempre es bonito venir a este campo, siempre agradecido. 
#AúpaAtleti,Con esta foto empiezan mis recuerdos de 2020. Hoy el año termina y ya nada será igual. Además de acordarnos de quienes se nos han ido y de ser más conscientes que nunca de que la salud es lo primero, este año tan difícil nos deja también muchos aprendizajes. A mí, 2020 me demostró que lo conocido no siempre es mejor que lo que queda por conocer; que el cómo y el porqué siempre son más importantes que el dónde y el cuánto; y que el trabajo duro y la conciencia tranquila son la causa y la consecuencia de una forma de entender la vida y el mundo. 2021, vamos a por ti. Gracias a todos y muchas gracias por vuestro apoyo y cariño,Trabajo, trabajo, trabajo 💪🏻⚽️
#AúpaAtleti 🔴⚪️,Ronnie, Marqués, KD, @paddy.8 y yo os deseamos FELICES FIESTAS A TODOS. 🎄❤️🐶🐶🐶,➕3️⃣ y ⚽. Noche perfecta. ¡Vamos! 💪😁🔴⚪ #AúpaAtleti

Caption text:
South Korean label, @gort_shop has now delivered Drop 2 of its Fall/Winter 2020 collection. The assortment features relaxed styles led by bandana marked PATCHWORK REVERSIBLE QUILTING JACKETS inspired by traditional Korean Hanboks along with the extra warm FISHTAIL PARKA WITH LINER that reimagines the design of an M-65 jacket. GORT’s FW20 Drop 2 is now available at @432hz.official.⁠⠀
Photo: Gort/432hz,@dior's taps internationally renowned artist, @peterdoig for its upcoming Winter 2021 collection. The finely tailored range features Doig’s swirling brushstrokes translated into embroidered accents and knit sweaters. Printings of Doig’s Milky Way are found atop a peak lapel coat while shirting and various accessories are dressed in prints of lion figures. The vibrant imagery plays off the subverted militaristic codes, juxtaposing Doig’s gentle artwork against camouflaged anoraks and waistcoats. View all of Dior's Winter 2021 offerings by hitting the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Dior,@berniesanders has just released a crewneck design based on his viral pose at the recent Presidential Inauguration. The senator from Vermont has playfully responded with the launch of a simple black sweatshirt that plasters the comical image of himself across the front. Adding to the look is his personal “Bernie” logo printed on the lower right corner of the garment.⁠ The “Chairman Sanders” Crewneck is now available at the Bernie Campaign store for $45 USD, with all of the proceeds going towards Meals on Wheels Vermont.⁠
Photo: Bernie Campaign Store,@evisenskateco and @independenttrucks have teamed up for a concise graphic-filled capsule. The assortment includes a lineup of hoodies, anoraks, and graphic T-shirts. One standout piece is a multi-paneled anorak arriving in black, white, or olive. Co-branding from both labels is placed on the upper right sleeve over the anorak’s white panel, complete with twin waist pockets, and drawstrings at the hood. The collaboration will be available on January 23 on Evisen Skateboards’ website, ranging from ¥4,000 – ¥27,000 JPY (approximately $36 – $260 USD).⁠⠀
Photo: Evisen Skateboards,@fearofgod has now readied the introduction of its 2021 “Seventh Collection.” Included in the range is a celebration of the 100th-anniversary of the Negro Leagues. The tribute to the origins of baseball arrives in the form of a vintage baseball pullover jacket and henley tees featuring textured velvet flocking typography. Also included are elevated T-shirts, sweatshirts, and hoodies featuring a new iteration of the brand’s FG logo in a military-inspired stencil font. The “Seventh Collection” is set to drop in the coming week exclusively on the Fear of God website.
Photo: Fear of God,@carharttwip has revealed the lookbook for its Spring/Summer 2021 collection. The latest offering fuses the brand’s classic workwear and utilitarian influences with nods to the great outdoors and a selection of everyday staples. Workwear references vary from the continued use of robust canvas as a central material to the inclusion of new camouflage patterns. The collection's core everyday pieces range from triple stitch sweats to classic Single Knee Pants as well as graphic tees and hoodies. For a full look at the collection, hit the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Nicola Roman Walbeck,@steveaoki‘s @dimmakcollection and @playboy have teamed up for a special six-piece capsule. The limited pieces combine both Playboy and Dim Mak’s iconic branding and include two short sleeve t-shirts, two long-sleeve t-shirts, and two hoodies. The collection pays homage to Dim Mak Records’ founding year, with the number “96” featured in the graphics, while reflecting Aoki’s silhouette donning an Oni Menpo Samurai mask. The Playboy x Dim Mak collaboration collection is now available exclusively on @playboylabs.⁠⠀
Photo: Carter Jung & Josh "Midjordan" Farias,@driesvannoten is “dressing for our days” as seen through his Fall/Winter 2021 collection. Rife with rich textiles and flourishes, the range is cut looser than Van Noten’s previous efforts, blending elements of formality and sportswear in a relaxed hybrid that feels appropriate for endless days spent working from home. View more of the looks via the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: Dries Van Noten,@elirusselllinnetz’s @erl__________ has envisioned an extensive assortment of playful garments rooted in Linnetz’s desire to create an effortless contemporary wardrobe for Fall/Winter 2021. Titled “The Final Frontier,” the range consists of signature pieces such as boxy hoodies, woven base layers, corduroy trousers that mingle with more progressive pieces, like metallic silver quilted outerwear and shearling-trimmed shirting. Get the full preview via the link in bio.⁠⠀
Photo: ERL,@asaprocky has showed off a new decorative set of grillz made with real flowers. Crafted by @grillzjewelz_is_right, the piece features a white gold base riddled with natural pink and canary yellow VVS diamonds for a striking top and bottom contrast look. Flowers have been suspended in a resin and embedded in two of the teeth, matching the colors of the surrounding stones. ⁠Swipe to get a closer look.⁠⠀

Bio: Black Lives Matter ✊🏿
Caption text:
“Seguimos juntos”

Um ano tão marcante e desafiador como o anterior, nos permite ter mais certeza o que é mais importante na nossa vida: saúde e família. Ao longo desses 10 episódios, vocês conheceram melhor a mim, minha história, meus pensamentos e objetivos, mas também as pessoas da minha vida. Sem elas, e sem vocês, nada disso seria possível. Que 2021 seja mais alegre, mais leve, mas principalmente, mais saudável! Tamo junto, Vini.

#ViniForReal

\\

“We’re all in this together”

A year as challenging as the previous one, allows us to get a clearer picture of what are the most important things in life: health and family. Throughout these 10 episodes, you were able to get to know me, my history, my thoughts and goals, but also the people in my life. Without them, and without you, none of this would be possible. May 2021 be happier, more peaceful, but above all, healthier! We're all in this together, Vini.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Happy New Year!!! 🤍🤍🤍,“Consciência”

A nossa responsabilidade começa na tomada de consciência das nossas ações e das suas consequências nas outras pessoas e na sociedade. É surreal que na atualidade continuem a existir tantos casos de racismo, de injustiça social, de irresponsabilidade ambiental, entre muitas outras coisas, ... O bom exemplo constitui o melhor e mais eficaz sistema de educação. A mudança começa em cada um de nós.

#ViniForReal 

\\ 

“Conscience”

Our responsibility begins in the awareness of our actions and their consequences on other people and in society. It’s surreal that today there are still so many cases of racism, social injustice, environmental irresponsibility... Setting a good example is the best and most effective education system. The change starts within each one of us.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Feliz natal! Gratidão e esperança que logo vamos voltar a nos abraçar normalmente. Que tenham uma grande noite com a família de vocês! ♥️🎅🥂🔥 #Familia🖤,“Voltar mais forte”

Para um jogador de futebol, as lesões são momentos de dúvidas, incerteza e insegurança. Mas no futebol como em todas as outras coisas da vida, a glória não está em nunca cair, mas em se levantar a cada vez que caímos.

#ViniForReal

\\

“Coming back stronger”

For a football player, injuries represent doubts, uncertainty and insecurity. However, the greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Madrid es blanca! 😁🤍
Partidazo del equipo para cerrar una gran semana! 

Madrid is white! 😄🤍
A big performance to end a great week!,“Novo cenário”

Uma nova realidade, um país diferente, outro idioma, novas rotinas, outras exigências, novos rivais... vir para Madrid representou tudo isso. Um momento de mudança e adaptação delicado que é mais fácil de atravessar com o apoio constante da sua família e dos seus amigos.

#ViniForReal 

\\

“A new stage”

A new reality, a different country, another language, new routines, higher demands, new rivals... coming to Madrid represented all this. A time of change and adaptation that is easier to go through with the constant support of your loved ones.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Vamoooooos equipo!! Partidazo y a octavos!! Esto es el Madrid! 💪🏾🤍

Well done lads!!! Great performance and into last 16!! This is Real Madrid! 💪🏾🤍,“Origens - parte 2”

“Quando faz com amor, é impossível dar errado...tem que dar certo.”.
O Flamengo foi e sempre será uma das grandes paixões da minha vida. Independentemente do que acontecer no resto da minha carreira, nada apagará o orgulho e a honra que eu sinto por ter jogado com a camisa rubro negra.

#ViniForReal

\\

“Origins- part 2”

“You can't go wrong when you do things with love.”
Flamengo was and always will be one of the greatest passions of my life. Regardless of what happens in the rest of my career, nothing will erase the pride and honour I feel for having played with the red and black shirt.

#ViniForReal

\\

Caption text:
@hypegolf: @footjoy has introduced the HyperFlex BOA Golf Shoe featuring high-tech innovation, performance, and supreme comfort. The golf shoe is designed for longevity and features a BOA Fit System that initiates a WRAPID structure that blankets a form fit throughout the foot. Its configuration refines stability in the shoe without sacrificing elasticity. The silhouette is also equipped with a proprietary StratoFoam cushioning system for support, while also catering to a golfer’s need for energy return. These are set to release sometime in February for $180 USD. Click the link in bio for more info.⁠⠀
Photo: Footjoy,@blondey and @adidas have returned for its fourth see-through Superstar collaboration. Taking on a classic “Core Black/Cloud White” colorway, the uppers are crafted from a partially translucent jet black TPU, and overlaid with a white Three Stripe graphic, white heel tab with black branding, and a gold “Blondey” midfoot stamp. Though the upper may appear somewhat delicate at first glimpse, Blondey told HYPEBEAST that it’s in fact much more durable than standard skate shoe materials. Pick up a pair come January 30.⁠⠀
Photo: adidas,@snipes_usa celebrates its new Brooklyn store opening with "Dunks Since 1985" Pop-Up Museum. Nestled in the center of the 6,000 square foot converted bank, the pop-up museum consists of 35 ultra-rare and influential @nike Dunks, ranging from artist collaborations to seminal @nikesb styles and much more all provided by @projectblitz. The display will be on until February 28. Click the link in bio for more info.⁠ Which is your favorite Dunk? 
Photo: Nick Llanton/HYPEBEAST,@newbalance continues its slew of 2002R releases with a duo of colorways. Originally released in 2002 as New Balance’s most innovative running sneaker, this updated 2002R boasts the same brand technologies as the original with the ABZORB cushioning and N-ERGY in the midsole resulting in an almost identical aesthetic. Both pairs feature premium pig suede uppers ensuring the quality that New Balance is known for. Expect these to release within the coming months.⁠⠀
Photo: New Balance,@jumpman23 has unveiled a Spring-ready colorway of the Air Jordan 1 Mid in "Dutch Green." The upper of the shoe is expressed in two tones of green accompanied by pink laces adding a sleek colorblocking to the upper of the shoe. While black Swooshes, pink Jumpman tongue tags, printed Wings motifs on the collars, and insoles serve as a nice touch of detail to finish off the look. Look for these to arrive within the coming weeks.⁠⠀
Photo: Nike,@adidas continues its goal towards sustainability by bringing PRIMEGREEN construction and a playful take on the classic Stan Smith silhouette with Earth-centric graphics reminiscent of Sean Wotherspoon's “Superearth” collaboration. Uppers are built of mostly white leather with the highlight being a colorful collage of graphics that reach from the forefoot to the heel and encompass everything from flowers to raindrops, a globe, and a hand-stenciled Trefoil logo. The shoe is available now via @atmos_japan for approximately $116 USD.⁠⠀
Photo: atmos⁠,A new look at a @sacaiofficial x @jpgaultierofficial x @nike Vaporwaffle has surfaced online as we near Chitose Abe’s debut for Jean Paul Gaultier couture. Sporting a familiar double-stacked midsole and doubled up Swooshes, the couture-focused shoe features an upper that boasts nylon, suede and leather, all split by Air Footscape Woven-like black or white stitching that runs across the midfoot and toebox. Catch it in action during Abe’s first Gaultier runway.⁠⠀
Photo: @sneakerjamz_new,@asics has unveiled a new GEL-QUANTUM 180 silhouette alongside the launch of its Spring/Summer 2021 “ENGINEERED FOR EVERYDAY” campaign. Tapping LA-based photographer @camhicks_ and London-based furniture designer @modularbymensah, the new shoe sees an aesthetic makeover on the upper featuring a mesh toe box with leather overlays similar to their running models. Look for it to come in two colorways on January 22 via the ASICS website and official stockists for approximately $170 USD each.⁠⠀
Photo: ASICS,@jumpman23 is prepping a take on the Air Jordan 1 Low reminiscent of the @diamondsupplyco x @nike Dunk Low “Tiffany.” Dubbed “Tropical Twist,” this iteration carries the same two-tone look found on the 2005 release and features a teal leather base accented by black overlays and a matching nylon tongue. Branding comes in the form of gradient Swooshes, color-matched tongue tags, printed insoles, and tonal black embroidered Wings motifs at the rear. Stay tuned for official release details.⁠⠀
Photo: Nike,@realcoleworld and @puma have officially announced the DREAMER 2 hoops shoe. Coming in an inaugural “January 28” colorway, the model features abstractly shaped overlays with a blend of leather, suede and synthetic materials in a louder yellow hue. The bottom sole unit is coated with black, while hits of red make its way onto the pods on the outsoles. Expect it to be available via PUMA’s NYC Flagship Store, website, and select stockists worldwide on January 28 for $135 USD.⁠⠀

Caption text:
OFFICIAL: The #FIFA21 Team of the Year has been announced.,Using @footballmanager, we've explained what a Libero is, where the term comes from, the attributes needed for the role, the best tactics to use and even suggested some players you might want to try in the role, from elite picks to wonderkids and a budget option. #FM21,#SquawkaScout x @footballindex: @rodridepaul 🔎⠀
⬡⠀
One of the most versatile creative midfielders in European football, Rodrigo De Paul is just as dangerous in a withdrawn No.8 role as he is as a No.10.⠀
⬡⠀
In this gallery, you can see his stats compared to central midfielders and attacking midfielders in both roles via the radar templates.⠀
⬡⠀
Blessed with fantastic technique, the Argentine is relentless in his ball progression. He can be seen driving his team into the final third from deeper positions before whipping well-executed crosses and penetrative passes into the box.⠀
⬡⠀
We’ve used the calendar year of 2020 to provide some context for his stats so none of the rankings will change.⠀
⬡⠀
Last year, RDP ranked in the top three in Serie A for chances created, Big Chances created, take-ons completed, passes into the area and passes into the final third.⠀
⬡⠀
RDP also had the highest Expected Assist value in the Italian top-flight, despite only registering six assists - you can play his team-mates. ⠀
⬡⠀
But he doesn’t just progress the ball with his passing, he can dribble the ball up the pitch and into the area himself. Completing the second-most take-ons in Serie A in 2020, he also ranks highly for carries into the final third and carries into the penalty area.⠀
⬡⠀
We’ve also included his defensive coverage. Not only is RDP brilliant in possession, he puts in a shift for his team all over the pitch when looking to get the ball back.⠀
⬡⠀
A playmaker entering his peak years and currently playing for a bottom half Serie A side, the Argentine is definitely someone to keep an eye on. He might even be attracting interest from your favourite club already⠀
⬢⠀

Caption text:
Sextou, galera! 🚀 Quem aí também não aguenta ouvir uma batida que já sai dançando?,Papo reto, galera! 👇
⠀
Uma pessoa neurodivergente é alguém com desenvolvimento neurológico atípico ou destinto, ou seja, é diferente daquilo que a nossa sociedade considera como padrão. Autismo, TDAH, dislexia e discalculia são consideradas condições neurodivergentes.
⠀
Pessoas com essas condições podem ter crises que acontecem, em sua maioria, como uma reação a uma sobrecarga sensorial/emocional, ansiedade ou situações estressantes. Se você presenciar um momento de crise, foque em acalmar a pessoa ao invés de tentar descobrir a causa. As informações desse post foram retiradas do guia informativo feito apenas por pessoas autistas, o www.guia-autismo.carrd.co -
Parabéns, galera! A informação é grande aliada da inclusão e do respeito.

#pracegover: Em um fundo cinza está escrito: “Como ajudar quando uma pessoa com desenvolvimento neurológico atípico estiver em crise: Pergunte se você pode encostar nela para oferecer carinho e conforto; Respeite caso a pessoa queira ficar sozinha e não queria sua ajuda; Pergunte se ela quer dar uma volta ou se quer ir embora; Evite falar de você e não diminua o que a pessoa está sentindo; Pergunte se tem alguma coisa que você possa fazer para ajudar.",Eu e meu cavalinho @andersonaguia espancamos essa dupla. A prefeitura do Rio tomou a iniciativa de colocar as pessoas com deficiência, acima dos 18 anos, que vivem nessas habitações na lista de prioridades para receber a vacina. Há exatos 20 anos (18/01/2001), @romariofaria marcava o terceiro e último gol do Vasco na vitória por 3-1 sobre o São Caetano, pela final do Campeonato Brasileiro. Conquistava, ali, seu primeiro e único titulo nacional atuando no país. De quebra, garantia sua primeira (de três) artilharia do Brasileirão: 2000, 2001 e 2005.,Por ofício, solicitei ao governo e prefeitura do Rio de Janeiro que incluam as pessoas com deficiência e doenças raras nas primeiras fases de vacinação contra o COVID-19. 

Apesar de amplo esforço do Congresso e da minha luta como senador, essas pessoas não foram incluídas como prioritárias no plano de vacinação. 

O mesmo apelo faço a todos os governadores e prefeitos do país, que tenham sensibilidade e dêem prioridade à vacinação de pessoas com deficiência e doenças raras.

Caption text: @goatsneakers: The Women’s Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘Starfish’ updates the classic silhouette, taking inspiration from the material and build of an astronaut’s space suit. A crisp white base, replete with perforated detailing on the toe box, is contrasted by overlays in a vibrant ‘Coast’ blue finish. Nike branding on the heel tab and woven tongue tag arrive in University Gold for a nice color contrast. Available on the app and GOAT.com,The Nike Dunk High SB ‘MF DOOM’ embraces the late and legendary underground rapper with intricate details and artwork. The upper consists of black suede with Midnight Fog leather overlays and a faux ostrich skin toe area, accented with reflective piping. An MF Doom mask graphic adorns the tongue tags, while ‘Doom’ embroidery appears on the collar. Red laces offer a bold contrast, anchored by ‘SPR’ and ‘VLN’ lace dubraes while MF Doom artwork graces the sockliner and outsole.,@goatsneakers: Paris-based creative agency Studio FY7 teamed up with New Balance on the classic 992 silhouette. It all rides on a split black and white ABZORB midsole, offering lightweight cushioning and a smooth ride. Available on the app and GOAT.com,Cozy, cooler. Bio: Experience the world through the eyes of National Geographic photographers.
Caption text:
Video by @joelsartore / A Lear’s macaw eyes the camera during a Photo Ark shoot @loroparque. Named after Edward Lear, an artist who was famous for painting macaws during the mid-19th century, this is one of the most mysterious birds on Earth. For more than a hundred years, nobody knew where Lear’s macaws lived in the wild. The mystery was solved in 1978 with the bird being re-discovered in the Bahia state of northeast Brazil. At the time, only 60 birds remained, but thanks to the work of many environmental groups and government agencies, there are more than a thousand worldwide today.  #macaw #endangered #PhotoArk #savetogether,Photo by @laurakmorton / Commercial fishing vessels are seen docked along the waterfront in San Francisco, California’s Fisherman’s Wharf neighborhood. While the neighborhood is consistently ranked the city’s number one visitor destination, behind the tourist-focused businesses an essential fishing industry still operates there. Millions of pounds of seafood come through the wharf annually, and the wharf's Pier 45 houses the West Coast's largest concentration of commercial fish processors and distributors. Supported by @InsideNatGeo’s Emergency Fund for Journalists I am currently working on a project on the Fisherman’s Wharf neighborhood to document the economic issues created by the COVID-19 pandemic, which are affecting communities relying on tourism around the globe. For more from this story and photographs of people, places, and culture follow along @laurakmorton.,Photo by @erintrieb / A scene of skiers on Park City Mountain, Utah. Despite nationwide closures and travel bans throughout the U.S., most states' ski resorts remain open for the season, with social distancing and face-covering requirements in place. For more stories from around the world follow @erintrieb.,Photo by @celestesloman / This is a virtual portrait of Christiana Neazer, from Rialto, California, who lost her husband, Michael Neazer, to COVID-19. The 30-year-old nursing school student is pregnant with their child, due on March 15, which would have been the couple's sixth wedding anniversary.

In December and January I documented six families that lost relatives to the COVID-19 pandemic. Writer Katie Sanders explores what it means to say goodbye from a distance, whether that is a hazmat suit, via Zoom, or through text message. For this project I was also documenting at a distance, creating virtual portraits from my studio in Brooklyn.

Since it was too risky to travel and take these portraits in person, we decided to create virtual portraits from my Brooklyn studio. This approach seemed fitting because the story focuses on distance, separation, and communication through devices, so I created a still-life setup with my iPad surrounded by white flowers, to commemorate those lost. I FaceTimed with each of the families and directed them in the frame while I took photographs of the setup.

Check out Nat Geo's link in bio for more on this story.,Photos by Michael Yamashita @yamashitaphoto / The Great Wall meets water in the Panjiakou reservoir. The reservoir was created after the Luan River was dammed in the late 1970s, submerging sections of the wall and turning farmers into fishermen. In times of drought, more wall is exposed as the lake level drops. Fishermen cast their nets over the submerged sections as the wall acts like an artificial reef attracting the fish stocked in its waters. The Panjiakou reservoir supplies water to the Tianjin Province. #panjiakou #panjiakoureservoir #greatwall #greatwallofchina #reservoir,Photo by @paulnicklen / As winter turns to spring in Antarctica's Ross Sea, baby penguins poke tiny beaks through delicate eggshells and begin exploring their vast new polar surroundings. Meanwhile, four-foot-tall, 80-pound parents consider the precious fruit of their months-long labor with great curiosity. I am awestruck by the unfaltering dedication and commitment emperor penguins demonstrate for their young—they are fascinated by their chicks and marvel at every moment. Follow me @paulnicklen to see how love belongs to every species. #penguin #emperorpenguin #rosssea #antarctica #fascination,Photo by Luján Agusti @lujanag / Eagle Pass, Texas, United States. Portrait of Maverick County Sheriff Tom Schmerber, who spoke out against Trump's anti-immigrant measures and declares, "I can see why people are running away from persecution. Maybe they are just looking for a better life." Follow me at @lujanag to learn more about this and other stories.

Check out Nat Geo's link in bio for more on this story.,Photo by @simonnorfolkstudio / Photographed on my second assignment for National Geographic magazine, twelve years ago, Naqsh-e Rustam is the acropolis of the great Persian kings of the 5th and 4th century BCE, with the high tombs of Darius II, Ataxerxes I, and Xerxes I. The site is near the ruined city of Persepolis in western Iran. In the foreground is the mysterious Ka’be-ye Zartosht, which has been thought to be either a tomb, a sacred library, or possibly a chamber for the keeping of holy fire. Follow me @simonnorfolkstudio for updates, outtakes, unpublished, and archive material. #archaeology #iran #Persia #Persianempire #Achaemenidempire,Photo by @nicholesobecki / At the Burao camp for internally displaced persons, a woman watches a swarm of locusts darken the sky. Erratic climate conditions that cause severe droughts across the Horn of Africa in some years yield extreme rainfall in others—the trigger, in 2019, for the worst outbreak of desert locusts Somalia has seen in decades. The locusts can devour a field of crops in hours. As National Geographic and @everydayeverywhere explore how difficult, fraught conditions around the world are pushing women from their homes, I returned to Somaliland and Kenya, where the climate crisis is a major driver. To see more of my work on humanity’s connection to the natural world, please follow @nicholesobecki.

Check out Nat Geo's link in bio for more on this story.,Photo by Daniella Zalcman @dzalcman / If you tuned into the U.S. presidential Inauguration yesterday, you would have heard Amanda Gorman read "The Hill We Climb," at 22 the youngest inaugural poet in American history. This portrait is from 2017, when she was named the first ever National Youth Poet Laureate. "Somehow we’ve weathered and witnessed a nation that isn’t broken, but simply unfinished," her poem reads. "We, the successors of a country and a time, where a skinny black girl descended from slaves and raised by a single mother can dream of becoming president only to find herself reciting for one."

To my family, friends and fans who keep me going, please know that I will never take your support for granted. 

Create your #OpenToBetter pledge at www.coke.co.uk/opentobetter and set your resolution for 2021 #ad,I’ve got a game tomorrow so need to sign off here but before I go I wanted to reflect on what has been the most challenging year. I’ve been so proud to see people coming together to help those in need and that same compassion needs to continue into 2021 because it’s people like you that make this country great and there is still so much more work to do. We have shown the difference we can make when we unite. Don’t look back on this year thinking you haven’t achieved anything, you achieved everything. You survived 2020. Your strength was tested and you made it. Give yourself a pat on the back. I’m hoping in 2021 I get to celebrate in the crowd with you again, I really just miss that, I can’t believe none of you got to be with me for the Leipzig hat trick but hoping there will be many more. Everything I have achieved this year has been our achievement I couldn’t have done it without your support. Let’s aim and hope for an equal playing field for all in 2021. Love to you all. Be safe and a happy new year. MR x,😁❄️,It wasn’t pretty but good to close out the year with a win 💪🏾,Here’s why I do it. Now, why do you do it? O Esporte Interativo agora é TNT Sports! Continue seguindo a gente na @tntsportsbr

Essa é a nova marca de esportes da WarnerMedia e será a integração da produção de conteúdo na América Latina. Com a mudança, todas as mídias e plataformas digitais que o Esporte Interativo está presente passam a estar com novo nome: @tntsportsbr. A linguagem, a qualidade do conteúdo produzido e a interação com o fã seguem no dia-a-dia e passam a romper fronteiras do Brasil.

Continuaremos na cobertura com linguagem que você torcedor se identifica, falaremos aquilo que os fãs estão comentando e, mais importante, queremos seguir sendo a voz do apaixonado por esportes. Tanto no dia-a-dia nas principais notícias e assuntos, quanto na transmissão do Brasileirão, UEFA Champions League, Nations League, Campeonato Italiano... Além do Último Lance, Melhor da Liga, Liga Espetacular e De Olho na Liga.

@highsnobietydesign: For this month's design feature multidisciplinary design studio @sixnfive shares a look at its latest venture, @sixnfiveobjects exploring industrial design through digital and physical mediums. #hsdesign,@highsnobietymusic: This week on Highsnobiety Soundsytem 50, we join @youngdolph in celebrating the finer things with the deluxe edition of his Rich Slave project. On the track "Large Amounts," the Memphis rapper perfects the art of showing out. Meanwhile, @smino vibrantly honors Martin Luther King Jr. day with his track "MLK DR." And up-and-coming multidisciplinary artist @loshhaje releases the hypnotic, jazzy "Faji."⁠⠀
⁠⠀
Hit the link in bio to listen.,@_thibo shares a closer look at a set of @dior Winter Snow Boots, which just made their debut at the house's Winter 2021 collection.⁠
⁠
They are a continuation of the @dior Snow Slipper from the 2020 Ski Capsule, featuring Dior's all-over oblique on a quilted technical fabric. #hskicks,@dingyun_zhang is the gift that keeps on giving. This time, the designer partnered with 3D artist @antonitudisco for 3D-rendered film stills and animations that feature exaggerated versions of Zhang’s puffers and YEEZY sneakers set in utopian landscapes.⁠
⁠
It was a case study to show how the brand could build buzz outside of traditional big-budget runway shows and large-scale advertising campaigns. It worked, with the first set of images getting up to three times as much as engagement as usual.⁠
⁠
"I would like to premiere my new capsule collection in collaboration with Antoni, in a two part series," says Zhang. "They further explore the fantasy and possibilities of extreme sports and weather conditions, and show [followers] how my garments exist within that world."⁠
⁠

📷: @julientell,Throughout his career, the late artist Robert Smithson drew abstract floating objects and varied formless masses. Thought of as studies for his famous “earthworks,” these drawings are resonant on their own as depictions of nowheres — spaces suspended in abstraction that hit differently in the era of video conferencing. ⁠
⁠
Presented in collaboration with the @holtsmithsonfoundation as a special project for “Not In Paris,” critic and art historian Mostafa Heddaya wades through the mud of Smithson’s work, as well as that of the brilliant partner he predeceased by a half century, artist Nancy Holt. Hit the link in bio to join him on this journey. ⁠
⁠

Caption text:
If you were asked to think of a football prodigy who didn’t make it, there’s a fair few you could choose. Freddy Adu, Hachim Mastour, Michael Johnson, but what if we told you these are the lucky ones?

While they never reached their potential, they MADE it; part of the 0.012% of academy players to actually have a professional career. Which begs the question - what happens to the remaining 99.988%?

Can you imagine giving your life to a dream and having it disappear in an instant. They find themselves chasing the shadows of who they once were.

This brilliant film, produced by former Welsh International @max_certifiedsports, and VO’d by former Crystal Palace Academy player @1lowki, gives a voice to those who were previously anonymous, the players who we and the academy systems forget about.

Watch the short film on COPA90 Stories YouTube [link in bio] and make sure to follow @certifiedsports for more.,Happy 48th to the original goalscoring goalkeeper — Rogério Ceni ⚽️🧤

132 career goals 🤯,The journey @manlikecolinkazimrichards is on is unrivalled...

If Jay-Jay Okocha was so good they named him twice, then we don’t what to say about this guy. Colin Kazim-Richards? C. Kâzım? Colin Kâzım? Colin Kâzım Kâzım? The Coca-Cola kid? Not many have had a career like him.

Born in East London, Kazim-Richards came through Arsenal’s academy, before being released and moving north to Bury. In 2005 he joined Brighton for £250k, with the fee being paid for by a fan who won a Coca-Cola competition.

Kazim-Richards only spent one season at Brighton, who finished bottom of the Championship. After relegation he went to Premier League Sheffield United, and when they went down, he started his globetrotting tour. The first stop was Fenerbahçe, but after falling out with their board and having his contract ripped up, he signed for Galatasaray, which didn’t go down particularly well…

After spending some time at Toulouse, in 2012, Kâzım Kâzım was then loaned out to Olympiacos, where he won the Greek Super League (and bleached his hair). He spent the 2012/13 season at Blackburn, scoring the goal that knocked Arsenal out the FA Cup, before joining Bursaspor in the summer of 2013. After one season Kazim-Richards was on the move again, rocking up at Feyenoord. Here he really hit form there, netting 13 times in the 2014/15 season.

In February 2016 he joined Celtic, where he helped them win the Scottish Premiership, but then decided to switch up continents. Going to Brazil made sense, as his wife Mariana is from São Paulo. He first went to Coritiba, moving onto Corinthians after six months.

Kazim-Richards thought he may as well see Mexico before coming back to Europe. In 2018 he was loaned to Lobos BUAP, later playing for Veracruz and Pachuca. Now 34, Kazim-Richards is back in the UK once again with Derby. Here he’s managed by Wayne Rooney, who he played against for Sheffield United in 2006.

That gives you an idea how long he’s been around. And he’s still scoring. Keep it going Coca-Cola Kid 🙌,Our third and final stop in The Crossover series.

#WinAsOne @easportsfifa,To become the youngest player to represent Manchester United since Duncan Edwards in 1953, you must have something about you.

When @angel.gomes10 ran onto the Old Trafford pitch on 21st May 2017, there was a huge roar as he replaced Wayne Rooney. This youngster who fans had heard so much about - captaining England’s U16s, U17s and U18s - was finally going to get his break.

Fast forward three years and things hadn’t progressed as planned. Gomes had only appeared four more times in the Premier League, and left a month later when his contract expired on 30th June 2020.

In August, Gomes signed for Lille before being loaned to Portuguese side @boavistafutebolclube for this season. Back in the homeland of his dad, Nani’s Godson has recorded three goals and five assists in 11 games. We urge you check out his solo strike v Farense, it’s rather good.

Boavista might currently be bottom of the Primeira Liga with just one win, but Gomes’ performances and flourishing form might just make United regret letting him go...,@carlytelford1 and @sio_chamberlain put goalkeeping in women’s football into perspective.

To one of the greatest. To my hero. It was a dream come true to play alongside you. Congratulations on the most unbelievable career. The 🐐 Happy Retirement @waynerooney ♥️,This year, I will continue to be #OpenToBetter 

To my family, friends and fans who keep me going, please know that I will never take your support for granted. 

Create your #OpenToBetter pledge at www.coke.co.uk/opentobetter and set your resolution for 2021 #ad,I’ve got a game tomorrow so need to sign off here but before I go I wanted to reflect on what has been the most challenging year. I’ve been so proud to see people coming together to help those in need and that same compassion needs to continue into 2021 because it’s people like you that make this country great and there is still so much more work to do. We have shown the difference we can make when we unite. Don’t look back on this year thinking you haven’t achieved anything, you achieved everything. You survived 2020. Your strength was tested and you made it. Give yourself a pat on the back. I’m hoping in 2021 I get to celebrate in the crowd with you again, I really just miss that, I can’t believe none of you got to be with me for the Leipzig hat trick but hoping there will be many more. Everything I have achieved this year has been our achievement I couldn’t have done it without your support. Let’s aim and hope for an equal playing field for all in 2021. Love to you all. Be safe and a happy new year. MR x,😁❄️,It wasn’t pretty but good to close out the year with a win 💪🏾,Here’s why I do it. Now, why do you do it? Share your Why in the comments below 👇,Not the result we wanted in the end. Time to kick on...,Reflecting on what WE have achieved this year and the work still to be done. So grateful for the steps we have taken forward and everyone who has played a role in that. I’m grateful to my family and loved ones for always encouraging me to use my voice and to football for allowing me to live out my dream every day ♥️ Taking a minute to count my blessings today, Merry Christmas everyone, we’ve just about made it to the end of 2020. Love to you all. MR x,For everyone who, over the last 12 months, has stepped in to support our most vulnerable children, thank you. This is for you ♥️,Scottyyyyyy 🤩
Today was a good day ♥️

Bio: Black Lives Matter ✊🏿
Caption text:
“Seguimos juntos”

Um ano tão marcante e desafiador como o anterior, nos permite ter mais certeza o que é mais importante na nossa vida: saúde e família. Ao longo desses 10 episódios, vocês conheceram melhor a mim, minha história, meus pensamentos e objetivos, mas também as pessoas da minha vida. Sem elas, e sem vocês, nada disso seria possível. Que 2021 seja mais alegre, mais leve, mas principalmente, mais saudável! Tamo junto, Vini.

#ViniForReal

\\

“We’re all in this together”

A year as challenging as the previous one, allows us to get a clearer picture of what are the most important things in life: health and family. Throughout these 10 episodes, you were able to get to know me, my history, my thoughts and goals, but also the people in my life. Without them, and without you, none of this would be possible. May 2021 be happier, more peaceful, but above all, healthier! We're all in this together, Vini.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Happy New Year!!! 🤍🤍🤍,“Consciência”

A nossa responsabilidade começa na tomada de consciência das nossas ações e das suas consequências nas outras pessoas e na sociedade. É surreal que na atualidade continuem a existir tantos casos de racismo, de injustiça social, de irresponsabilidade ambiental, entre muitas outras coisas, ... O bom exemplo constitui o melhor e mais eficaz sistema de educação. A mudança começa em cada um de nós.

#ViniForReal 

\\ 

“Conscience”

Our responsibility begins in the awareness of our actions and their consequences on other people and in society. It’s surreal that today there are still so many cases of racism, social injustice, environmental irresponsibility... Setting a good example is the best and most effective education system. The change starts within each one of us.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Feliz natal! Gratidão e esperança que logo vamos voltar a nos abraçar normalmente. Que tenham uma grande noite com a família de vocês! ♥️🎅🥂🔥 #Familia🖤,“Voltar mais forte”

Para um jogador de futebol, as lesões são momentos de dúvidas, incerteza e insegurança. Mas no futebol como em todas as outras coisas da vida, a glória não está em nunca cair, mas em se levantar a cada vez que caímos.

#ViniForReal

\\

“Coming back stronger”

For a football player, injuries represent doubts, uncertainty and insecurity. However, the greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.

#ViniForReal

\\

ES: video con subtítulos en español en mi página de Facebook,Madrid es blanca! 😁🤍
Partidazo del equipo para cerrar una gran semana! 

Madrid is white! 😄🤍
A big performance to end a great week!,“Novo cenário”

Uma nova realidade, um país diferente, outro idioma, novas rotinas, outras exigências, novos rivais... vir para Madrid representou tudo isso. Um momento de mudança e adaptação delicado que é mais fácil de atravessar com o apoio constante da sua família e dos seus amigos.

#ViniForReal 

\\

“A new stage”

A new reality, a different country, another language, new routines, higher demands, new rivals... coming to Madrid represented all this. A time of change and adaptation that is easier to go through with the constant support of your loved ones.

#ViniForReal

\\

“Quando faz com amor, é impossível dar errado...tem que dar certo.”.
O Flamengo foi e sempre será uma das grandes paixões da minha vida. Independentemente do que acontecer no resto da minha carreira, nada apagará o orgulho e a honra que eu sinto por ter jogado com a camisa rubro negra.

#ViniForReal

\\

“Origins- part 2”

“You can't go wrong when you do things with love.”
Flamengo was and always will be one of the greatest passions of my life. Regardless of what happens in the rest of my career, nothing will erase the pride and honour I feel for having played with the red and black shirt.

#ViniForReal
